Ibikorwa by'ubwandu bwa coronavirus (COVID-19) mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu k'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, kuva ku itariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Imibare y'ubwandu bw'icyorezo cya coronavirus (COVID-19) igaragaza imiterere ihuriyeho hagati y'ibihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'ibihugu bikorana n'u Bwongereza, igaragaza ko nubwo icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri mu byiciro bitandukanye mu bihugu bitandukanye, kirimo kwiyongera ku buryo bwihuse ku isi hose.
Nk'uko byagenze mu Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bikeneye kongera uburyo bwo kwitegura kubera umubare wiyongereye w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi, cyane cyane ubuvuzi bukomeye.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, abantu banduye icyorezo cya pnemoniya kitaramenyekana bagaragaye mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyo mu Bushinwa cyatangaje ko iyi ndwara yatewe na virusi ya coronavirus itaramenyekana aho yaturutse, ubu ikaba izwi nka severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 yahawe izina ry'indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko hafi 80% by'abanduye COVID-19 bagira uburwayi bworoheje, ni ukuvuga indwara z'ubuhumekero zifite cyangwa zidafite imibu, kandi abenshi muri bo bakira.
Mu bice bigera kuri 14%, COVID-19 iba indwara ikomeye cyane ikeneye kwitabwaho mu bitaro, naho 6% iba ikomeye cyane ikeneye kwitabwaho mu bitaro.
Umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bapfuye mu gihe cy'imiti ni 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye uko ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwagiye bwiyongera muri buri gihugu cyo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'ubukungu k'Uburayi (EU/EEA) no mu Bwongereza (UK) maze tugereranya n'uko byari bimeze mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Turagereranya kandi imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 muri iki gihe mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza n'u Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 yakwirakwiriye mu bindi bihugu, kandi icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bindi bice by'isi cyakurikiye iki gihugu.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, umuyobozi mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo cyugarije isi.
Mu itangazo ry'umwaka wa 2020 rya Eurosurveillance ryo ku wa 5 Werurwe, Spiteri na bagenzi be bavuze ku bantu ba mbere banduye COVID-19 mu Burayi nk'uko bitangazwa na OMS.
Muri EU/EEA, abarwayi ba mbere babonetse mu Bufaransa ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 ubwo bari baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, COVID-19 yari imaze kugaragara mu bihugu 30 bigize EU/EEA na UK, aho kuva ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza uyu munsi, abarwayi 39,768 n'abapfuye 1,727, mu gihe abarwayi 17,750 n'abapfuye 1,441 bari mu Butaliyani honyine.
Kubona umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 n'ubwinshi bw'abandura COVID-19 uko bigenda byiyongera
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC), gitangaza imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 muri buri gihugu ku isi, binyuze ku makuru y'ibiro by'ubuzima, ibiro bya OMS n'ibiro by'ishami, buri munsi saa mbiri za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma COVID-19 muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, hagereranywa n'ibyabaye mu Butaliyani.
Mu rwego rwo kubara umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakira, twabaririje imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu gihe cy'iminsi 14, mu bihugu byose bigize EU/EEA na UK, kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Nanone kandi, twerekanye umubare w'abanduye buri gihugu ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa mbiri za mu gitondo ugereranyije n'uw'u Butaliyani ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama.
Imyitwarire ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK
Imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza muri rusange yakurikiye iy'intara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza muri rusange, imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 yatangiye kwiyongera ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, maze igera ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Icyumweru).
Ibi byatewe n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'imibare y'abandura muri Italiya, ariko ibihugu byose bigize EU/EEA hamwe n'Ubwongereza byagize ukwiyongera kw'abandura COVID-19 bahuriyeho (Inkomoko).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama-15 Werurwe 2020.
Ivuga ko ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa mbiri za mu gitondo, ibihugu 15 byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA n'ibindi 15 byo mu Bwongereza byari bifite umubare w'abanduye nk'uw'u Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu gusa cyangwa munsi yaho.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu bigaragaza ko umubare w'abandura COVID-19 wiyongera cyane mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK.
Imibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 igaragaza ko iki cyorezo cyugarije ibihugu byose.
Ibi biracyari uko nubwo ibihugu bifite uburyo butandukanye bwo kuvura, hamwe n'ibanze bitandukanye by'uburyo bwo kumenya niba umuntu arwaye ndetse n'uburyo butandukanye bwo guhitamo abantu bagomba gupimwa COVID-19, harimo no kongera umubare w'abantu bapimwe.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu bice by'u Butaliyani byibasiwe n'iki cyorezo bavuze ko 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi bukomeye, kandi amakuru avuga ko ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bukomeye muri utwo turere byuzuye.
Umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 barwariye mu bitaro no/cyangwa mu byumba by'ubuvuzi bukomeye ku kigero cya EU/EEA ni 6% na 1% gusa (amakuru ntabwo agaragara).
Ahubwo, ibyo bigomba gutangwa mu buryo buhuje n'amakuru agaragaza umubare w'abarwayi n'abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2010-2011 bwagaragaje itandukaniro rinini hagati y'ibitanda by'indembe n'iby'indembe mu Burayi, aho mu Budage hari ibitanda 29.2 na 4.2 kuri buri baturage 100.000 muri Porutugali.
Ibyo bisobanura ko hari ibihugu bifite ubuvuzi buhagije cyangwa buke ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (ibitanda 12,5 by'indembe z'indembe ku baturage 100.000 mu 2010).
Ibyago byo kubura ibikoresho by'ubuzima bishingiye ku kigereranyo cy'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari mu bitaro muri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA na UK ndetse n'ikibazo cy'uko umubare w'abari mu bitaro by'indembe urenga 90%, byerekanwa mu cyegeranyo cya gatandatu cy'icyegeranyo cyihutirwa cy'ibyago bya COVID-19 cy'Ikigo cy'Umuryango w'Abibumbye Gishinzwe Ubumenyi n'Iterambere (ECDC).
Kubera ko abarwayi bakomeje kugaragara mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'ibihugu bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bukomeye bigakorera mu turere tw'akarere, amakuru y'abarwayi n'ibitaro by'ubuvuzi bukomeye yagombye kuboneka mu buryo bwa Nomenclature of territorial units for statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Ibyabaye mu Butaliyani n'ibiri kuba mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje kwiyongera ku buryo bwihuse mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK.
Ku bw'ibyo, ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bukomeye bigomba kwitegura ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 mu baturage no kwiyongera kw'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi, cyane cyane ubuvuzi bukomeye, kugeza aho byifashe mu bice by'u Butaliyani byibasiwe n'iki cyorezo.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe mu bushakashatsi bw'ubutabazi bw'ibihe byihutirwa bwakozwe na ECDC, kwitegura neza ni ngombwa mu guhagarika ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2, ndetse no mu guhindukira kuva mu guhagarika ikwirakwira kugera mu gukiza, kuko kwiyongera byihuse kw'umubare w'abarwayi byitezwe ku buryo budafite ubushobozi butuma abayobozi n'ibitaro bihabwa umwanya uhagije wo gusobanukirwa, kwemera no gushyira mu bikorwa ingamba zikenewe mu gihe zitashyizweho hakiri kare.
Ubushakashatsi bw'ibanze bugaragaza uburyo bwo kwita ku buzima bufite akamaro mu guhangana n'iki kibazo.
Hari impande nke zifite ubushobozi bwo kongera imbaraga mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya igitutu cy'ubuvuzi.
Iyo bitabaye ibyo, biteganyijwe ko serivisi z'ubuvuzi mu bindi bihugu bya EU/EEA zizagorwa n'umubare wiyongereye w'abarwayi bakeneye ubuvuzi bukomeye mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19), cyateje indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,000, ndetse n'abantu barenga 80,000 bamaze kwandura mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu, bituma habaho ibyago bikomeye ku baturage.
Kimwe na virusi ya SARS-CoV, yatumye abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi bafatwa na SARS mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora gukwirakwizwa mu bihaha kandi igatanga ibimenyetso nk'ibyo.
Nyamara, COVID-19 ntabwo ari ingume nka SARS kandi yica abantu bake ariko ikwirakwira cyane kandi igera ku bantu bakuru n'abagabo kurusha abakobwa n'abasore.
Mu gusubiza ibinyamakuru byinshi byatangaje iby'iyo ndwara, iyi ngingo igamije gutanga ibisobanuro birambuye ku birebana n'ibyo byatangajwe.
Tuzasuzuma ibintu by'ibanze biranga indwara, impamvu zitera, za mikorobe, uko zishobora kugenzurwa, uko zakoreshwa mu kuvura, uko zavugwa mbere y'igihe n'uko zakwirindwa.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bikeneye ibisubizo, twizeye ko ubu bushakashatsi buzatuma dusobanukirwa neza indwara y'ibicurane kandi tukayirwanya.
Umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi wo ku wa 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye umunsi utazibagirana ku Bashinwa basabwe kuguma mu ngo zabo mu gihe cy'iminsi mikuru yose ndetse no mu byumweru byakurikiyeho kubera icyorezo cy'indwara iterwa na virusi itaramenyekana.
Iyi virusi imeze neza neza nka coronavirus (CoV) yatumye habaho indwara y'ubuhumekero (SARS) mu 2003; ku bw'ibyo, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryise SARS-CoV-2 ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, kandi indwara iteza iyi ndwara yitwa CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Iyi ndwara yatangiriye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, ihita ikwira mu gihugu hose no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi yari imaze kwandura abantu barenga 80.000 banduye COVID-19, abagera ku 40.000 bakize naho abagera ku 3.000 barapfuye.
OMS iraburira ko COVID-19 ari umwanzi w'abantu wa 1 kandi ko ishobora kuba iteje akaga kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) ibivuga, mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, hamaze gutangwa inyandiko zirenga 200 ku cyorezo cya COVID-19 zirimo amakuru ajyanye na virusi, indwara, icyayiteza, uburyo bwo kuyigenzura n'uburyo bwo kuyivura, kuva raporo ya mbere yo ku wa 7 Mutarama 2020 yabonetse, igaragaza ko hari ubwoko bw'imiterere ya virusi yavuye mu barwayi batandukanye.
Iki cyigisho kigamije gukomeza ubushakashatsi bukorwa muri iki kibuga gishya kigenda kigera ku mibare myinshi.
Mu gihe cy'ubutaha, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS hamwe n'indi ndwara ya CoV, Middle East respiratory syndrome (MERS, yavutse mu mwaka wa 2012).
Nanone kandi, tuzasuzuma ibyo twize ku birebana no kwirinda indwara, ibyo abantu batekereza, n'ibibazo by'ingenzi tudafite ibisubizo.
CoVs zari zarafashwe nk'agakoko gato cyane katagira ubukana ku bantu, kagize uruhare mu guhitana abantu bagera kuri 15% by'abandura indwara zisanzwe 4.
Ahubwo, muri iki kinyejana, twabonye virusi ebyiri za CoV ziteye ubwoba ku bantu, ari zo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatangiriye mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, zihita zikwirakwira mu bindi bihugu zigatera indwara n'urupfu.
COVID-19 iriho ubu ni CoV ya gatatu yongeye kugaragara mu mateka azwi y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragara ku ishusho. ku ishusho.1,1, abarwayi b'indwara y'igituntu bataramenyekana aho baturuka, batangajwe bwa mbere muri Wuhan ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kuri Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima y'Ubushinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, basanze icyorezo cya CoV.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, habonetse umuntu wa mbere wanduye indwara ikomeye i Wuhan.
Muri icyo gihe, iyo ndwara yakwirakwiriye mu migi yari ihakikije, mu bihugu.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama, havumbuwe ko abantu bashobora kwandura iyo ndwara binyuze mu gutandukana n'abandi.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan warafunzwe, kandi ingendo rusange zahagaritswe.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwagaragaje ko mu bantu 41 banduye, 21 gusa ari bo bagaragaye ku isoko ry'amafi rya Wuhan, aho bivugwa ko icyorezo cyaturutse ku nyamaswa itaramenyekana.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubukungu ku isi.
Mu gihe iyi raporo yandikwaga, iyo ndwara yari imaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa no mu bihugu bigera kuri 50 byo hirya no hino ku isi (Igishushanyo (Igishushanyo.2).2).
Uko imimerere igenda ihinduka, ingaruka n'uburemere bw'ikibazo biracyari kure.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 8,866 bagaragayeho 4,021 banduye COVID-19 bwatumye haboneka ibisobanuro bishya by'icyorezo cy'ubwandu (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 ibasira abantu b'imyaka yose ariko bafite hagati y'imyaka 30 na 65.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri (47.7%) cy'abanduye bari bafite imyaka iri hejuru ya 50, bake cyane bari munsi y'imyaka 20, naho abarwayi 14 gusa bari munsi y'imyaka 10.
SARS-CoV-2 yari ifite umubare munini w'abagabo (0.31/100.000) ugereranyije n'abagore (0.27/100.000).
COVID-19 ikomeje kwiyongera mu baturage kurusha mu karere ka Hubei.
COVID-19 imaze iminsi 5 (2-9) kuva itangiye kugeza igihe igaragajwe.
Ibimenyetso by'iyo ndwara byamaze iminsi igera kuri 4,8 (3.0-7.2).
Igihe cy'urupfu rwe cyamaze iminsi 9,5 (4.8-13).
Umubare w'ibanze w'abarwayi b'abagabo (R0) wari 3.77 (95% CI: 3.51-4.05), naho R0 yahinduwe yari 2.23-4.82.
Umubare w'abanduye wazamutse mbere ya 23 Mutarama 2020, bitewe n'ubwiyongere bw'abantu bari mu ngendo mbere y'umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi mu Bushinwa.
Abapfuye bari 1.44% (IC 95%: 1.10-1.86%), naho umubare w'abapfuye wahinduwe ku gipimo cya 3.06% (IC 95%: 2.02-4.59%).
Ibibazo bitatu by'ingenzi bya COVID-19 byari iby'igitsina (abagabo), imyaka (≥60), n'imyimba ikomeye.
