Glycoprotein (S) yanduye ifata ingirabuzimafatizo 2 (ACE2) na dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4) za SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, mu cyiciro cy'imiterere, bityo ingirabuzimafatizo zombi zikagira uruhare mu guhangana.
Uduce tw'imiterere ya RNA twanduye twoherezwa mu ngirabuzimafatizo; nyuma yo kwanduza, uduhimba tw'imiterere ya RNA tw'imiterere ya glycoproteins na nucleocapsid twubaka udukoko twanduye, tukaba dufatanya n'amaraso kugira ngo dukureho virusi.
Ubuhinduzi bwa mbere bwa SARS-CoV-2 bwagaragaye ku itariki ya 10 Mutarama 2020.
SARS-CoV-2 yagaragaye ko ari ubwoko bushya bwa beta-CoV bufite imiterere ya 99.98% mu bipimo 10 byafashwe mu isoko rya Huanan ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja i Wuhan, aho iyi virusi ya mbere yabonetse.
SARS-CoV-2 ifite ingirabuzima fatizo zimeze nka SARS-CoV kurusha MERS-CoV.
Hakoreshejwe ibikoresho by'ishusho, ibice bya SARS-CoV-2 byabonetse mu bice by'umuhanda wa gari ya moshi.
Inzayi za ACE2 zabonetse mu buryo bwa SARS-CoV-2 hamwe na SARS-CoV.
Ahubwo, poroteyine S ya SARS-CoV-2 ifata ingirabuzimafatizo za ACE2 ariko ntiyiyunga nk'uko bimeze kuri SARS-CoV, ibyo bikaba bihuje n'uko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubukana buke mu bantu ugereranyije na SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kandi gukora poroteyine ngufi itari yigeze iboneka, ishobora kwitwa orf3b na poroteyine isohoka, ishobora kwitwa orf8.
orf3b ya SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba ari yo ituma abantu barwara kandi ikanabuza IFNβ kugaragara; ariko, orf8 nta kintu gifatika igira.
Ku itariki ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Zhou na bagenzi be bagaragaje uburyo bwo gukora cryo-EM buhagije bwa enzymes ACE2 ku bisubizo bya 2.9 Å muri amino acide B0AT1.
Basanze uyu mubumbe, ugizwe n'ibinyabutabire bibiri, wari ufite imiterere ya molecule ya atome imwe kandi ACE2-B0AT1 ishobora guhuza poroteyine za S, ibyo bikaba byerekana ko nta cyorezo cya CoV na kimwe cy'ubwandu.
B0AT1 ishobora kuba ari yo igamije kuvura indwara ziterwa n'imiti ya SARS-CoV-2.
Aho byavuye
Birazwi ko SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV byombi byaturutse ku nyamaswa z'inkazi, kandi ko byanduriye ku bantu binyuze mu nyamaswa z'inkazi n'ingamiya, mu gihe zikwirakwiza.
Mu kugereranya SARS-CoV-2 na izindi virusi za CoV, bat-CoV-ZX45 na bat-CoV-ZX21 ni byo byitwa ko byoroshye gutwara SARS-CoV-2 kuko iyi virusi ihura na SARS mu buryo bwa 96%
Ahubwo, inyamaswa nyayo yatumye abantu bashobora kurenga iyo nzitizi, n'inzira yanyuragamo ntiziramenyekana.
Ji na bagenzi be batekereza ko inzoka zakwirakwije virusi mu bantu binyuze mu guhanahana imiterere ya S protein.
Nk'uko ubushakashatsi bwakozwe, abashakashatsi bo mu mujyi wa Guangzhou mu Bushinwa bagaragaje ko ingona - inyamaswa y'ikirura irya ibikoko ikunda gukoreshwa mu buvuzi gakondo bw'Abashinwa - ishobora kuba ari yo yandura SARS-CoV-2 ikajya mu bantu, hashingiwe ku buryo ingona na SARS-CoV-2 bihuriye ku kigero cya 99% mu buryo bw'imiterere.
Ahubwo, itandukaniro ry'igice cya 1 ku ijana hagati y'imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo ebyiri ni rinini cyane; bityo rero, ibimenyetso by'ukuri ntibiragaragara (Igishushanyo cya 33).
Ibyinshi mu bimenyetso bya SARS-CoV-2 biracyari ibisanzwe.
Virusi za SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zishobora kumara amasaha 48 mu cyuma cyumye n'iminsi 5 ku bushyuhe buri hagati ya 20°C na 40%-50%.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba ifite izindi ngorane.
SARS-CoV-2 yagaragaye ko idashobora guhangana n'imirasire y'izuba (ultraviolet rays) ku bushyuhe bwa 56 °C mu gihe cy'iminota 30; ku kigero cya 75%, imiti irimo chlorine, peracetic acid, calcium, n'ibindi bintu by'umwimerere, ariko atari chlorhexidine, ishobora kwica virusi.
Abantu muri rusange ntibagira ubudahangarwa bwo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 bityo bashobora kwandura iyi virusi.
Kugeza ubu nta bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku cyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2.
Ku bw'ibyo, dushobora kwifashisha gusa ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mbere ku birebana na za virusi za CoV, cyane cyane SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV (Igishushanyo (Igishushanyo 4).4).
Ubusanzwe, iyo virusi igeze ku nyamaswa idashobora kugenda, ubutumwa bwa mbere bw'iyo nyamaswa bufatwa binyuze mu byitwa "pattern recognition receptors" (PRRs) birimo "C-type lectin-like receptors", "Toll-like receptor" (TLR), "NOD-like receptor" (NLR), na "RIG-I-like receptor" (RLR).
Iyo virusi ikora ingendo zitandukanye, ituma habaho imikorere, iterambere ry'ingirabuzimafatizo za dendritic, no gukora interférons z'ubwoko bwa I (IFNs) zibuza ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo, bityo bigatuma macrophage idashobora kurwanya virusi.
Ahubwo, poroteyine N ya SARS-CoV ishobora gufasha mu gutandukana n'imbeba.
Bidatinze, ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo guhangana n'ubwandu buhinduka, bukongera imbaraga mu kurwanya virusi.
T lymphocytes, ari zo CD4+ na CD8+ T cells, zifite uruhare rukomeye mu kurwanya virusi.
Uturemangingo twa CD4+ T dutuma uturemangingo twa B dutangira gukora intwaro z'ubwirinzi, naho uturemangingo twa CD8+ T tukicisha uturemangingo tw'umubiri twanduye.
Utwo tugingo duto cyane twitwa T helper twubaka za cytokine zifasha mu kurwanya indwara.
Ahubwo, virusi ya CoV ishobora gutuma uturemangingo twa T tudakora neza, bigatuma dupfa.
Imiti irwanya indwara yitwa humoral, harimo poroteyine nka C3a na C5a n'umubiri wa virusi, na yo ni ingenzi mu kurwanya iyi virusi.
Urugero, udupande tw'umubiri twavanywe mu murwayi wakize twagize ingaruka ku murwayi wa MERS-CoV.
Ku rundi ruhande, iyo umuntu afite imitsi myinshi, bituma habaho imyuka myinshi (free radicals) yangiza ibihaha n'izindi ngingo, rimwe na rimwe bigatuma ingingo nyinshi z'umubiri zidakora neza, ndetse rimwe na rimwe zikapfa.
Virusi ya SARS-CoV-2, yabonetse mu bantu ba mbere, igaragara ko yibasira cyane abantu bakuze bafite izindi ndwara n'abagore batwite.
Ubusanzwe, abantu bafite mikorobe cyangwa se bafite uturemangingo duke cyane, baba bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara kurusha abandi.
Igihe virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 imara igaragaza ibimenyetso ni iminsi 1-14, cyane cyane iminsi 3-7 dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi 425 ba mbere i Wuhan.
Ahubwo, ubushakashatsi bwakorewe ku barwayi 1.099 bwagaragaje ko muri rusange virusi imara iminsi 3 kugira ngo igaragaze ibimenyetso, mu gihe iminsi yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso iba iri hagati ya 0 na 24.
Ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa bwagaragaje ko iyo ndwara imara iminsi 4,8 (ku munsi wa 3,0 kugeza ku munsi wa 7,2), kandi ko yafashwe n'abarwayi 8.866.
Ni ngombwa ko abakozi b'ubuzima bashyiraho iminsi yo kwigunga bashingiye ku gihe nyacyo virusi imaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso, kugira ngo birinde ko abantu bafite virusi ariko badafite ibimenyetso byayo bashobora kwanduza abandi.
Ubusanzwe, abantu baba mu karere kabamo abantu banduye cyangwa bafite ubwandu, bagomba kumara iminsi 14 biherereye.
Ese igihe cyo guhagarika abantu ngo bagume mu ngo zabo kigomba kongerwaho iminsi 24?
Malariya ni ikimenyetso cy'ibanze cya COVID-19, gishobora kudakurikirwa n'ibindi bimenyetso cyangwa ibimenyetso birimo guhohoterwa, guhumeka nabi, ububabare bw'imitsi, gucibwamwo, umutwe, ububabare mu ijosi, ubunyoni, ububabare mu gatuza, guturika, guhumeka no gusama.
Bamwe mu barwayi bagize ikibazo cyo guhumeka nabi cyangwa se kubura umwuka mu maraso mu cyumweru kimwe nyuma yo kwandura.
Mu mimerere ikomeye, abarwayi bahitaga bagira ikibazo cyo kutagira amazi mu bihaha, bakagira umuvuduko w'amaraso uri hasi (septic shock), acidosis métabolique, na coagulopathy.
Abarwayi bafite malariya cyangwa ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero bw'indwara ya malariya, nubwo baba badafite ibibazo by'ibihaha, bagomba kugenzurwa hakiri kare kugira ngo bamenye niba bafite virusi.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu Ukuboza 2019 bwagaragaje ko 98% by'abarwayi bafite inyota, 76% bafite uruhu rwumye, 55% bafite ikibazo cyo guhumeka, na 3% bafite uburwayi bwo guhumeka; abarwayi 8% bakeneye imashini zifasha guhumeka.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi babiri b'umuryango umwe n'abarwayi baterwa intanga z'umuntu utari ufite ibimenyetso by'uburwayi, na byo byagaragaje ko ari uko bimeze.
Mu kugereranya, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu bantu mu 2012 bwerekanye ko abarwayi ba MERS-CoV bafite malariya (98%), guhumeka nabi (47%), no guhumeka nabi (55%) nk'ibimenyetso by'ingenzi.
