Imyotsi (26%) n'imihumetso (21%) na byo byagaragaraga mu barwayi ba MERS.
Mu barwayi ba SARS, indwara ya malariya (99%-100%), guhekenya umunwa (29%-75%), guhumeka nabi (40%-42%), guturika (20-25%), no guhagarara (13-25%) ni byo byavuzwe cyane, kandi 14%-20% by'abarwayi basabwaga gukoresha ibikoresho byo guhumeka.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, umubare w'abapfuye bashya ba COVID-19 wari ku kigero cya 2% mu gihe abamaze kwandura bose bari 66,576.
