Coronavirus yaturutse mu nyamaswa
Impinduka mu miterere y'ibinyabuzima zatumye virusi ya corona (CoVs) n'inyamaswa zirimo n'abantu, bihinduka mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi.
Mbere ya 2003, abantu bafite virusi ya CoV (HCoVs) ebyiri zari zizwiho guteza indwara zidakomeye, urugero nk'ibicurane bisanzwe.
Ibyavuye mu cyorezo cya Sars na Middle East respiratory syndrome (MERS) byahinduye ibintu, byerekana ko HCoV ishobora guteza akaga kandi ikabisha.
Icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 cyabaye mu Bushinwa hagati mu mpera za 2019, cyongeye kugarura virusi ya CoVs mu cyumba cy'uburuhukiro, kandi cyadutangaje kuko yashoboraga gukwirakwizwa mu buryo bwihuse kandi budahenze ugereranyije n'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV.
HCoVs zikomoka ku nyamaswa, bityo gusobanukirwa inkomoko ya HCoVs mu nyamaswa ni ingirakamaro.
HCoVs nyinshi zituruka mu bihaha kandi ntizitera indwara.
Hari ubwoko bw'inyamaswa na bwo buzwiho kuba ari bwo bwa mbere HCoVs zikora mbere yo kugera ku bantu.
Kumenya inyamaswa zitera indwara ni ingenzi mu kurwanya indwara zandura.
Gusuzuma imishyikirano iba hagati y'inyamaswa zifite virusi ya CoV na byo bishobora gufasha mu kumenya akaga ko kwandura virusi ya CoV mu bantu.
Muri iki cyigisho, turabanza dusobanure muri make ibyagezweho kuri HCoVs ndwi, twibanda ku mateka y'ibyavumbuwe n'inkomoko yabyo mu nyamaswa n'uburyo yakwirakwijwe hagati y'inyamaswa zitandukanye.
Muri iki gice, tugaragariza abantu bose uko HCoV zitandukanye zimeze, tureba n'uko zitandukana, tureba n'uko virusi ihinduka n'uko genome ihinduka.
Icyorezo cya CoV disease 2019 (COVID-19) cy'iki gihe ni cyo cyibanda kuri iyi ngingo.
Ikindi, uburyo inyamaswa zanduye zigira ubwandu n'uburyo ubwandu bwazo bugira ubwandu na byo birasuzumwa.
Virusi za corona (CoVs) ziri mu muryango wa Coronaviridae, igizwe n'urwego rw'ibinyabuzima byitwa viruses, buri bwoko bukaba bufite ibimenyetso by'umwimerere, kandi buri bwoko bukaba bufite umurongo umwe wa RNA.
Iyi virusi ifite ingirabuzima fatizo nini cyane ya 26 kuri 32 ya kilobases ya RNA, yitwaga CoVs kubera ko ifite ishusho y'ikamba iyo ibonetse mu cyuma cy'umushongi.
Mu byiciro by'inganda, CoVs zifite genomes zitari zahindutse kandi ziri hamwe.
Hafi bibiri bya gatatu by'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima bigizwe n'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima bibiri binini cyane (ORF1a na ORF1b), bigakora pp1a na pp1ab.
Muri ubwo buryo, poroteyine nyinshi zishobora kuvamo poroteyine 16 zitagira imiterere, zitwa nsp1~16.
Igice gisigaye cya genomic kigizwe na ORFs zigize poroteyine z'ibanze, zirimo spike (S), enveloppe (E), membrane (M) na nucleoprotein (N).
Poroteyine nyinshi z'inyongera (proteines accessoires) zigena umurongo w'ibanze w'ubwoko bwa CoV.
Dukurikije uko poroteyine z'ubwoko bumwe n'ubundi zimeze, virusi za CoV zashyizwe mu byiciro bine by'ingenzi (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV na delta-CoV), aho beta-CoV ari yo virusi ifite virusi nyinshi za HCoV kandi ikaba ifite ubwoko bune (A, B, C na D).
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe byerekana ko ibinyamushongo n'ibinyamushongo ari byo bikunze kuvamo virusi za alpha-CoVs na beta-CoVs, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zikunze kuvamo virusi za gamma-CoVs na delta-CoVs.
Mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi, CoVs zakomotse ku nyamaswa, kandi zimwe muri zo ni zo zitera indwara mu bantu.
Kugeza ubu, hamaze kumenyekana abantu barindwi bafite virusi ya CoV (HCoVs).
Muri izo, HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63 ni ubwoko bwa alpha-CoVs.
Indi beta-CoVs ya mbere ni HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, coronavirus y'indwara ifata imyakura (SARS-CoV), coronavirus y'indwara ifata imyakura yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS-CoV) na SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63 byibasira indwara zidakomeye, urugero nk'ibicurane bisanzwe n'indwara y'ibicurane.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ubwo, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 ziherutse kuvumburwa ni indwara z'ubukana, zigira ingaruka ku barwayi benshi cyane cyane mu gice cyo hasi cy'ubuhumekero, kandi hari ibyago byinshi byo guhura n'indwara yo guhumeka cyane (Acute Respiratory Distress Syndrome, ARDS) n'ingaruka zo hanze y'ibihaha (extrapulmonary manifestations).
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E, B814, bwavumbuwe mu maraso y'abarwayi bafite ibicurane bisanzwe mu myaka ya za 60.
Kuva icyo gihe, hari ibindi bimenyetso byagaragaye mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe kuri HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, byombi bikaba byerekana ibimenyetso by'ubwiyongere bw'uburwayi.
Mu by'ukuri, abantu benshi bemeraga ko ubwandu bwa HCoVs muri rusange butari bubi kugeza igihe habonekeye SARS.
SARS yadutse mu 2003 kandi ni imwe mu ndwara z'ibyorezo mu mateka ya vuba aha, aho yanduye abantu barenga 8.000, mu gihe 10% by'abapfuye byari byitezwe.
Nyuma y'imyaka icumi, indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS) yatumye icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane cyongera gukwirakwira mu bihugu byo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, kandi cyakwirakwira no mu bindi bihugu.
HCoV nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV), yaje kwitwa SARS-CoV-2, ni yo iteza icyorezo cya coronavirus cyugarije isi (COVID-19), kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,120 no kwandura abantu barenga 91,000 kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020.
Inanga zagiye zirasakuza kandi isi igomba kwitegura icyorezo cy'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2.
HCoVs zose uko ari 7 zituruka ku bibugu, ku bibugu cyangwa ku nyamaswa zo mu ngo.
Hari ibimenyetso byinshi bigaragaza ko HCoVs zose zikomoka ku mikorobe, aho virusi zisanzwe kandi zidakomeretsa ariko zifite imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo zitandukanye.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateye imbogamizi zikomeye mu buvuzi, siyansi, imibereho n'imyitwarire y'Abashinwa ndetse n'isi yose.
Gukurikirana inkomoko ya HCoVs mu nyamaswa bituma dusobanukirwa amateka, imiterere n'uburyo virusi ituruka mu nyamaswa imwe igera mu yindi.
Ibi kandi bishobora gutuma habaho kwihutisha igikorwa cyo gushakisha inyamaswa zitwara SARS-CoV-2 kuva mu nyamaswa, bigatuma abantu batandura.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, hatangazwa inkomoko ya HCoVs mu nyamaswa, ikwirakwira mu nyamaswa zitandukanye n'indwara ziterwa na zo.
By'umwihariko, twerekanye kandi tuganira ku ngingo rusange ivuga ko virusi ya HCoVs idashobora kugira ingaruka ku nyamaswa, ariko ko ishobora guteza akaga mu gihe imaze kwanduzwa mu nyamaswa.
Nanone, twasuzumye uburyo HCoV ihinduka iyo ikomeje kwiyongera, kandi ikagaragaza ko nta ngaruka igira ku ndwara.
Ingaruka z'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 cyo muri iki gihe na zo ziragaragazwa muri iyi nkuru.
Imibare y'ibinyabuzima byitwa CoVs yamenyekanye kuva mu myaka ya za 30.
Mbere y'uko virusi ya HCoV-229E yo mu bwoko bwa B814 ivanwa mu bice by'umubiri by'abantu banduye ibicurane, hari izindi virusi za CoV zari zaravumbuwe mu nyamaswa nyinshi zanduye, harimo inguge, imbeba, inka, ingurube, imbwa n'inka.
Mu binyejana bishize, hamaze kuvumburwa virusi zirindwi z'ubwoko bwa HCoV.
Amateka y'incamake y'ibanze y'ibanze ya HCoV mu cyiciro cy'ibanze (Igishushanyo cya 1) azagira icyo atwigisha.
HCoV-229E yagaragaye bwa mbere mu cyondo cy'abarwayi bari bafite ikibazo cyo mu gice cyo hejuru cy'umubiri mu mwaka wa 1966, kandi yagaragaye ko ikura mu maraso y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere.
Abarwayi banduye HCoV-229E bagaragaje ibimenyetso by'icyorezo, birimo umutwe, gucibwamwo, gucibwamwo mu ijosi, malariya no gukorora mu barwayi 10~20%.
Nyuma mu 1967, HCoV-OC43 yagaragaye mu buryo bwo guhinguranya ingingo, nyuma yo gutangira gukoreshwa mu bwonko bw'ibinyamushongo.
Ibimenyetso bya HCoV-OC43 bisa n'ibya HCoV-229E, ariko ibimenyetso byayo ntibigaragara mu bindi birwara by'ibicurane nk'ibicurane bya A na rhinoviruses.
HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 byombi bigenda hirya no hino ku isi, kandi bikunze kugenda cyane mu gihe cy'imbeho mu gihe cy'ikirere giteye ubwoba.
Muri rusange, iyo mikorobe yombi imara igihe kitageze ku cyumweru igaragaza ibimenyetso, ikurikirwa n'igihe cy'uburwayi cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu bitangiye gukora ubushakashatsi, abantu barwaye HCoV-229E barwaye indwara zidakunze kwibasira abantu.
Abarwayi bake bari bafite imitsi mike ni bo bakomeretse cyane mu gice cyo hasi cy'igituza.
SARS, nanone izwi nka atypical pneumonia, ni yo ndwara ya mbere y'icyorezo cy'ubwandu bw'isi yose cyatewe na HCoV mu mateka y'abantu, kandi yatewe na SARS-CoV, virusi ya gatatu ya HCoV yavumbuwe.
Umuntu wa mbere wahuye na SARS mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2002 mu ntara ya Guangdong mu Bushinwa.
SARS imaze kwandura abantu 8,096 kandi ihitana abantu 774, ikwirakwira mu bihugu byinshi no ku migabane myinshi.
Uretse abantu bakunze kwandura, byitezwe ko buri murwayi ashobora kwandura abandi bantu babiri, ibimenyetso bikaba bigaragara mu minsi 4 kugeza ku minsi 7, naho umubare munini w'abanduye virusi ugasanga ari ku munsi wa 10 w'uburwayi.
Abarwayi ba SARS-CoV babanje kugira ibibazo by'ubuhumekero, umutwe, malariya, gucibwamwo no gucibwamwo, bikurikirwa n'ikibazo cyo guhumeka, guhumeka no kubona amazi mu bihaha.
Lymphopenia, ibipimo by'imikorere y'umwijima, n'umubare munini wa creatine kinase ni bimwe mu bibazo bya SARS byagaragaraga mu igeragezwa ry'ibipimo.
Ibikomere by'ibihaha (diffuse alveolar damage), kwiyongera kw'ingirabuzimafatizo za epithelial no kwiyongera kw'imikorere y'ibihaha byitwa macrophages na byo biraboneka mu barwayi ba SARS.
Hafi ya 20-30% by'abarwayi bakeneye ubuvuzi bukomeye n'ibikoresho by'ubuhumekero.
Uretse igice cyo hasi cy'umura, ibice byinshi by'ubuhumekero, umura n'impyiko na byo bishobora gukomereka muri ibi bihe bikomeye, akenshi bikurikirwa n'umuyaga w'imiti, ushobora gutuma hapfa abarwayi bafite uburwayi budafite ubushobozi bwo kwirinda indwara.
Virusi ya mbere yagaragaye mu mubiri wafashwe mu bihaha by'umuvandimwe w'umurwayi wa mbere wageze muri Hong Kong avuye mu mujyi wa Guangzhou.
Kuva icyo gihe, hashyizweho imihati myinshi mu bushakashatsi ku cyorezo cya HCoV.
HCoV-NL63 yagaragaye mu mwana w'amezi 7 wo mu Buholandi mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2004.
Mu mizo ya mbere, basanze ari indwara y'abana bato, abageze mu za bukuru n'abarwayi bafite uburwayi bw'ibihaha.
Kurwara indwara ya koryza, ibicurane, malariya, na bronchiolitis ni indwara zisanzwe ziterwa na HCoV-NL63.
Ubushakashatsi bundi bwagaragaje ko virusi imwe yabonetse mu bipimo by'amaso by'umwana w'umuhungu w'amezi 8 wari urwaye umusonga mu Buholandi.
Nubwo bwabonetse mu Buholandi, mu by'ukuri bwakwirakwiriye ku isi hose.
HCoV-NL63 bivugwa ko ari yo iteza 4.7% by'indwara z'ubuhumekero, cyane cyane mu ntangiriro z'impeshyi, mu itumba no mu itumba.
HCoV-NL63 ifitanye isano n'uburwayi bwo mu gatuza (obstructive laryngitis, cyangwa croup).
Muri uwo mwaka, HCoV-HKU1 yagaragaye mu mugabo w'imyaka 71 wari warakomeretse mu bwonko n'ubuhumekero muri Hong Kong.
Usibye ibicurane n'imikorere y'ibicurane, HCoV-HKU1 kandi yagaragaye ko ifitanye isano n'indwara y'igicuri.
Kimwe na HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 yabonetse ku isi hose, ituma habaho indwara ziterwa n'ubuhumekero budafite ubukana.
Iyi virusi ya HCoV ine yose irazwi kandi muri rusange ntizatuma habaho indwara z'ibyorezo, nubwo habayeho impanuka ziterwa n'ubwoko butaramenyekana bwa HCoV-NL63 y'icyorezo, iherutse kugaragara ko yateje impanuka zikomeye mu karere k'amajyepfo y'Ubushinwa.
Muri rusange, HCoVs zirushaho kugira ubushobozi bwo kugenda no gutura mu bantu, kandi zitangira kutagira ubukana.
MERS-CoV yagaragaye bwa mbere mu mwaka wa 2012 mu bihaha by'umurwayi w'imyaka 60 wari ufite ikibazo cy'uburwayi bw'umwijima n'impyiko muri Arabiya Sawudite.
Nubwo abantu bose bemejwe ko banduye bakomoka mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, abanduye baturutse mu bindi bihugu by'i Burayi na Tuniziya babonetse.
Mu mwaka wa 2015, muri Koreya y'Epfo hongeye kugaragara abantu 186 banduye.
Ibimenyetso bya MERS ni kimwe n'ibya SARS, harimo indwara y'ibicurane by'ubuhumekero.
Mu buryo butandukanye na SARS, abarwayi benshi ba MERS nabo bagaragaje uburwayi bw'impyiko, ubu MERS ni yo yonyine mu ndwara ziterwa na HCoV.
Abarenga 30% by'abarwayi bagira ibibazo byo mu gifu, urugero nko guhekenya no kwitsamura.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, abarwayi basaga 2500 bemejwe ko banduye bari bafite umubare munini w'abapfuye ugera kuri 34.4%, ibyo bikaba bituma MERS-CoV iba imwe mu virusi z'ubwandu zikomeye cyane mu bantu.
Mu kwezi k'Ukuboza hagati no mu mpera za 2019, abantu barwaye malariya bari bazwi ko barwaye SARS-CoV-2 babonetse i Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 cyugarije Isi ari ikibazo cy'ubukungu ku isi (Public Health Emergency of International Concern) kandi ko icyorezo cyiswe COVID-19.
Kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020, ku isi hose hari hamaze kugaragara abantu 90,053 banduye, naho 3,4% bapfuye.
Icy'ingenzi ni uko umubare w'abahitanwa n'iyi ndwara mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa ari 4.2%, mu gihe mu bindi bice by'isi ari 1.2%.
SARS-CoV-2 itera indwara z'uburwayi zikomeye cyane nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zirimo indwara ya malariya, guhumeka no guhumeka nabi.
Hari n'abarwayi bafite uburwayi bwo mu mutwe.
Igituntu ni kimwe mu bimenyetso bikomeye kandi bishobora kwiyongera vuba bigateza ibibazo mu muhanda wa gari ya moshi.
Nubwo SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 zifite imiterere isa cyane bitewe n'uko zifite imiterere isa cyane ya nukleyotide (high nucleotide sequence homology) igera kuri 82%, zigaragara ko ziri mu mashami atandukanye y'igiti cy'ibanze cy'imiterere (phylogenetic tree).
SARS-CoV-2 ni indwara y'uburwayi buciriritse ariko ikwirakwira cyane ugereranyije na SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Abantu bafite SARS-CoV-2 badafite ibimenyetso bamaze kugaragara kandi bishobora kubafasha kwihutisha ikwirakwira ryayo ku isi hose.
Kugereranya SARS-CoV-2 na HCoVs esheshatu zindi byerekana ko hari ibintu byinshi bihuriyeho n'ibindi bikeneye kumenyekana.
Icya mbere, igihe ibimenyetso by'iyi virusi bimara n'igihe ikiriho ni kimwe.
Muri ubwo buryo, SARS-CoV-2 ikurikiza imyitwarire y'izindi virusi esheshatu za HCoV.
Icya kabiri, ubukana bw'ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 ni hagati ya SARS-CoV na virusi enye za HCoV (ni ukuvuga HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63).
Ku ruhande rumwe, umuntu urwaye SARS-CoV-2 aba afite ibimenyetso bikunze kugaragara ku muntu urwaye HCoVs, harimo ibimenyetso bitazwi, bidafite imbaraga cyangwa nta bimenyetso na mba.
Ku rundi ruhande, umubare muto w'abanduye COVID-19 ushobora kugaragara nk'uko bimeze ku bantu bafite SARS-CoV, nubwo umubare wabo udakomeye.
Icya gatatu, SARS-CoV-2 na yo igaragaza imiterere y'ubwandu bwa HCoVs na SARS-CoV.
Ku ruhande rumwe, SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubushobozi bwo gukwirakwira cyane nk'uko bimeze kuri HCoVs.
Ku rundi ruhande, ntibiramenyekana niba SARS-CoV-2 yagabanutse nyuma yo kwanduzwa mu bantu nk'uko bimeze kuri SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Ku rundi ruhande, nk'uko bimeze ku zindi virusi za HCoV, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugaragara mu bipimo by'imiti.
Kuba SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura umuntu mu buryo butandukanye n'uko SARS-CoV ishobora kwandura mu buryo butandukanye, bigomba kwemezwa mu bushakashatsi buzakorwa mu gihe kiri imbere.
Ni ngombwa kandi kureba niba SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba yaragize igihe cyo kwihindura nk'uko bimeze kuri HCoVs.
Nubwo bimeze bityo ariko, amakuru ya SARS-CoV-2 arimo uko yakwirakwijwe, uko yafashwe n'uko yakomeje kugaragara mu bantu, azagira uruhare runini mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiriho ubu.
Ibimenyetso byoroheje biterwa na HCoVs byarahangayitse cyane.
Mu buryo butandukanye, birashoboka ko abantu bashobora kuba baragaragaje ubukana bw'iyi virusi ya HCoVs.
Mu yandi magambo, byombi bishobora kuba ari nk'ibikomoka ku cyorezo cya HCoV cy'ubwandu bwa mbere.
HCoVs ziterwa n'indwara z'ubwandu mu bantu n'abantu bafite ubwandu bukomeye bwa HCoVs zagiye zinyura mu bantu.
Kugira ngo ibyo bishoboke, HCoVs zigomba kwiyongera mu bantu kenshi bihagije kugira ngo umubare wiyongera w'abantu ukomeze kwihanganira ingaruka ziterwa n'umuntu cyangwa ikintu.
Muri ubwo buryo, uko SARS-CoV-2 igenda igabanuka kandi igakwirakwira mu bantu benshi, ni na ko amahirwe yayo yo kwandura abantu agenda yiyongera.
Iyo imaze kumenyera, gukwirakwira mu baturage biragoye guhagarika hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo gufunga cyangwa ubundi buryo bwo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Mu gihe cy'imyaka myinshi, hari ubwoko bune bwa CoVs bwagiye bukwirakwira mu bantu, butuma abantu bafite ubwandu bakunze kugira imbeho.
