Kugena uburyo bwo kwemeza umurwayi w'umuganga ufite COVID-19 ni ngombwa
Ku ya 6 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ryacu ryashyize ahagaragara amabwiriza yihutirwa yo gupima no kuvura abantu banduye icyorezo cya 2019 coronavirus (2019-nCoV), kandi ayo mategeko agaragaza ubuhanga bwacu n'uburyo bwo kurwanya icyorezo ku isi hose.
Ahubwo, coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) ni indwara nshya, ubumenyi dufite buzakomeza kwiyongera bitewe n'ibyagezweho mu bushakashatsi bukomeje no kuvugurura uburyo bwo kuvura; bityo rero, ibipimo n'imiti nabyo bizagenda bihinduka.
Muri iyi baruwa, twashubije ikibazo cy'imwe mu mabwiriza yacu kandi dutanga amabwiriza mashya yo gufata icyemezo cy'uko bizagenda n'amabwiriza mashya y'uko bizagenda ashingiye ku mabwiriza aheruka gusohoka mu gitabo cyitwa Diagnosis and Treatment Guidelines for COVID-19 (verisiyo ya karindwi)) cyatanzwe na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika ya Rubanda y'u Bushinwa.
Mu Ukuboza 2019, icyorezo cya coronavirus nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV) cyateye indwara, ubu ikaba yitwa coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) kandi ikaba yaranduye yitwa severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, OMS yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo cyugarije isi yose.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2, itsinda ryacu ryakoze ibyangombwa byihutirwa byashyizwe ku rubuga rwa Military Medical Research ku wa 06 Gashyantare 2020.
Kuva ayo magazeti yasohoka, abantu benshi barayakunze.
Ariko, birakwiriye ko tumenya ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, ubumenyi bwacu buzakomeza kwiyongera bitewe n'ibyagezweho mu bushakashatsi bukomeje no mu buvuzi; bityo rero, ibipimo n'imiti bizagenda bihinduka.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'ibyavuye mu gitabo cy'ibanze cy'ubushakashatsi n'ubuvuzi ku cyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatanzwe na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika ya Rubanda y'Ubushinwa (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), hagati ya 16 Mutarama 2020 na 3 Werurwe 2020, hasohotse ibitabo birindwi by'ubushakashatsi n'ubuvuzi, aho hari ibintu byahindutse.
Zhou na bagenzi be bavuze ko batangije uburyo bworoshye bwo gusuzuma indwara, bashingiye ku byo babonye mu bitaro.
