Ahubwo, akazi kabo gakeneye kuvugururwa hakurikijwe Itegeko Nshinga rishya ryo gupima no kuvura COVID-19 (Igitabo cya karindwi) n'ubushakashatsi bushya.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ibyavuye mu itangazo rya karindwi (3 Werurwe 2020), kwemeza umurwayi ukekwaho kwivuza bisaba ko umuntu ashyiramo kimwe mu bintu bibiri by'ibanze by'ubuzima bwe n'ibindi bibiri by'ibanze by'ubuzima bwe mu bitaro kugira ngo afate umwanzuro wa nyuma, cyangwa se bisaba ko umuntu asohoza ibintu bitatu by'ibanze by'ubuzima bwe mu bitaro mu gihe nta makuru y'ibanze y'ubuzima bwe asobanutse:
Amateka y'uburwayi: (1) kuba yarigeze gusura cyangwa kuba mu mujyi wa Wuhan cyangwa uturere tuwurimo, cyangwa uturere twaho hagiye haboneka abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu minsi 14 mbere y'uko ibimenyetso biboneka; (2) kuba yarigeze guhura n'abantu banduye SARS-CoV-2 (binyuze mu gupima aside ya nikeleyeri); (3) kuba yarigeze guhura n'abarwayi ba malariya cyangwa abafite ibibazo byo guhumeka mu mujyi wa Wuhan cyangwa uturere tuwurimo, cyangwa uturere twaho hagiye haboneka abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu minsi 14 mbere y'uko ibimenyetso biboneka; (4) kuba yarigeze guhura n'abarwayi banduye (abarwayi ≥ 2 barwaye ibicurane cyangwa se bari mu bigo by'ubuvuzi mu byumweru bibiri, urugero nk'amazu y'ubuvuzi, ibiro by'amashuri, amashuri, n'ahandi).
Ibimenyetso by'ubuvuzi ni: (1) malariya na/cyangwa guhumeka nabi; (2) ibimenyetso by'uburwayi byerekana ko umuntu yafashwe na COVID-19; (3) imibare y'ingirabuzimafatizo z'umubiri (white blood cells) igaragaza ko ifite ingufu, cyangwa se ko yagabanutse mu gihe cy'uburwayi bwa mbere.
Kugenzura kwa muganga bigomba gukorwa ku murwayi ukekwaho uburwayi cyangwa gusuzuma amazi y'umubiri nk'uko byashyizwe ahagaragara: (1) igihe ibizamini bya PCR byerekana ko umuntu yanduye SARS-CoV-2; (2) igihe virusi yose ya genome igaragaza ko isa cyane na virusi nshya ya coronavirus; (3) igihe ibizamini by'amazi y'umubiri byerekana ko umuntu afite IgM antibody na IgG antibody ya SARS-CoV-2; cyangwa igihe igisubizo cya SARS-CoV-2 cyavuye ku gisubizo kibi kigera ku cyiza, cyangwa igihe ibipimo by'amaraso byiyongereyeho ≥4 iminsi mu gihe cyo gukira kurusha igihe cy'uburwayi.
Turabona ko ibipimo bya PCR byihutirwa byo gusanga aside ya nucleic mu maraso cyangwa mu maraso byongewemo mu nyandiko ya kabiri (18 Mutarama 2020) na 22 Mutarama 2020.
Gushakisha amaraso byongerewe ku nomero ya kane (27 Mutarama 2020) no ku ya gatanu (8 Gashyantare 2020); naho ibipimo by'amazi yo mu mubiri byongerewe ku nomero ya karindwi.
Ubu buryo bushingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu rwego rwo gushaka uburyo bwo kuvura neza aside ya nucleic mu gihe cyo gupima vuba, hamwe n'ibipimo by'amaraso, byongereye ubushobozi bwo gupima, kandi byemeza ko kuba hari udusimba tw'umubiri ari kimwe mu byemezo by'uko umuntu yakira indwara.
Uretse ibyo, hari ibindi bimenyetso byinshi bitwibutsa ko tugomba kwitondera abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso bidasanzwe cyangwa badafite.
Ku bw'ibyo, icyapa cya Zhou na bagenzi be gikeneye kuvugururwa, kuko cyagaragazaga ko umuntu udafite ibimenyetso by'indwara ari we ufite amahirwe make yo kuyandura.
Iyo mibare kandi ikeneye kwemezwa mu bindi bitaro no mu bindi byiciro by'ubushakashatsi.
Muri make, twiringiye ko ibindi bimenyetso bifatika bizagaragara, kandi turasaba abasomyi kubivugaho.
Mu gihe tuzi ibyo twiteze n'ibyo twemeje, twiteguye gukurikiza no kubahiriza amategeko agezweho y'ibihugu byawe.
Itsinda ryacu rizasubizaho amakuru yacu mu gihe cyagenwe kugira ngo rigire icyo rigufasha.
Bangladesh yatangaje ko abantu batanu bandi bapfuye bazira COVID-19, ari na yo mibare ya mbere y'abantu bapfa buri munsi
