Kugeza ku munsi w'ejo, Ikigo cya Bangladesh gishinzwe kurwanya indwara z'ibyorezo n'ubushakashatsi (IEDCR) cyanditse ko abarwayi 114 bamaze gukira, 33 bakaba bari mu rugo.
