Amaduka yo muri Ositaraliya yashyizeho imipaka ku bicupa umuntu ashobora kugura rimwe
Ku cyumweru no ku wa gatandatu nimugoroba, amaduka yo muri Ositaraliya, Woolworths na Coles, yashyizeho imipaka ku bicuruzwa by'ibikoresho by'ubwoko bwose mu gihe umuntu agura ibyokurya bibiri cyangwa kimwe mu gihugu hose muri ayo maduka.
ALDI na yo yashyizeho imipaka y'uko ku wa Mbere hashobora kuba hari mushiki wacu umwe.
Ibi byahagaritswe byashyizwe ahagaragara mu butumwa bw'itangazamakuru ku mbuga nkoranyambaga za Facebook z'iyi sosiyete.
Abaguzi basabwe kwitegura kubera ubwoba bwa COVID-19 kuko abantu basabwa kwitandukanya.
Ku wa gatatu, Woolworths na yo yagabanyije kugura amagi yo kugura no kohereza mu rugo ku mafaranga y'igiceri kimwe ku munsi.
Ayo mavugurura akurikirana ku bihano bya mbere bya kane by'inguzanyo byatanzwe na Woolworths na Coles ku itariki ya 4 na 5 Werurwe muri izo sosiyete zombi mu gihe cy'amasezerano.
Mu nyandiko Coles yanditse ku ya 8 Werurwe, yavuze ko kugabanya ibicuruzwa by'ubucuruzi, "amaduka menshi yavuyeho mu gihe cy'isaha imwe gusa", avuga ko ibyo byasabaga "bitari bisanzwe", mu gihe ALDI, yanditse kuri Facebook ku wa kabiri, yavuze ko byari "bitunguranye".
Igiciro cy'ibicuruzwa cyazamutse cyane mu cyumweru gishize nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuvugizi wa Woolworths.
Iduka rya Costco ryo mu mujyi wa Canberra na ryo ryagabanyije umubare w'abavandimwe babiri mu cyumweru gishize.
Kugira ngo bagabanye ibura ry'ibikoresho, Coles yasabye ababikoresha gukora ibitabo byinshi kandi bakabikora kenshi, Woolworths ategeka ko byongerwa, naho ALDI igatanga ibindi nk'uko byari biteganyijwe ku wa Gatatu wihariye.
Russell Zimmerman, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishyirahamwe ry'abacuruzi ba ruganda muri Ositaraliya, yavuze ko abacuruzi bagerageza kongera ibicuruzwa ariko ko amategeko y'ubuyobozi ku kigero cy'imodoka zigurishwa yabatesheje imbaraga.
Yiteze ko amafaranga azakoreshwa azagabanuka, kuko abakozi ba leta bagerageza guhuza n'ibikenewe kandi bakagira iminsi mike yo gukora.
Ku wa kabiri, ALDI yatangaje ko nyuma yo gushyira hanze ibicuruzwa bizajya bigurishwa vuba, amaduka amwe n'amwe atazongera gukora ibintu bitandukanye ku wa gatatu.
Mu nkuru ya News.com.au, Dr Gary Mortimer, impuguke mu by'ubucuruzi bw'ibicuruzwa byo mu bwoko bwa "multi-store" (ubucuruzi bw'ibicuruzwa by'ubwoko butandukanye) wo muri Kaminuza y'ikoranabuhanga ya Queensland, yavuze ko amaduka atwara ibicuruzwa buri joro.
Yavuze ko iyo amagi ari manini, bituma ibiciro by'ayo acuruza bigabanuka, ku buryo iyo amaze gukendera, asigara ari amavuta menshi cyane, bigatuma abantu bumva ko hari ibyo bakeneye.
Russell Zimmerman, mu kiganiro cy'itangazamakuru cya ABC News, yavuze ko "Coles na Woolworths batekereza [ko] iyo hari ibintu byinshi mu isoko, ibicuruzwa nk'ibikoresho byo gukaraba mu bikombe n'ibikoresho byo gukaraba mu ntoki [bigurwa] bikaboneka mu bwinshi, ibyo bishobora kugabanya ubukana bw'ibyo bintu".
Umwe mu bakozi bakora mu ruganda rw'amatungo y'intama, yatangaje kuwa gatatu ko ayo matungo yarangiye.
Kimberly-Clark, ukora ibirungo, na Solaris Paper ukora Sorbent, bemeje ko bakorana 24/7 kugira ngo bagere ku byo bakeneye, nk'uko raporo y'ikinyamakuru News.com.au ibigaragaza.
Urubuga rwa interineti Domain.com, rugurisha amazu, rwavuze ko hari abacuruzi batanga ibirahuri by'ubuntu ku mukinnyi wa mbere w'umukino wa hammer muri Melbourne, aho hari hagurishijwe ibirahuri bike kubera ko abaguzi bari bafite ikiruhuko mu mpera z'icyumweru kirekire, harimo n'umunsi w'abakozi.
Mu makuru yo kuwa kane yo mu kinyamakuru cya buri munsi cy'i Darwin cyitwa NT News, harimo igitabo cy'imfashanyigisho ya Bibiliya kigizwe n'ibitabo umunani bigomba gukurwaho kugira ngo gikoreshwe nk'ibikoresho byo gufunga.
Amazu y'ubucuruzi yabanje kwanga gushyiraho imipaka, nk'uko byatangajwe na ABC Australia ku wa 3 Werurwe aho bavugaga ko batateganyaga gushyiraho imipaka y'ubucuruzi.
Russell Zimmerman yongeyeho ko hari n'ibindi bicuruzwa biboneka ku isoko birimo ibiyobyabwenge, ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki, ibiribwa byumye, isabune n'ifu.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, hanze ya Ositaraliya, ku mugoroba wo ku cyumweru, ikigo cy'ubucuruzi cyo kuri interineti cyitwa Ocado cyagaragaje ko abantu batemerewe kugura amakarito ya Andres, mu gihe umuntu yaguraga hagati y'amagati 2 n'amagati 12.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo cyugarije isi yose
Ku wa gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19  ari indwara iterwa na virusi ya coronavirus SARS-CoV-2  ari icyorezo cyugarije isi yose.
Nubwo ijambo "icyorezo cyugarije isi" ryerekeza ku burwayi bwugarije isi, aho kwerekeza ku ndwara z'ibyorezo, OMS yagaragaje ko leta zigomba kwita ku bibazo by'abantu:
"Ibihugu byose bishobora guhindura uko iki cyorezo cyugarije isi.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, yavuze ko "iyo ibihugu byibanda ku cyorezo, bigasuzuma, bigakira, bigashyira abantu mu byiciro, bigakurikirana kandi bigashyira hamwe".
"Twumvise duhangayikishijwe cyane n'uburyo iyi ndwara ikwirakwira, n'ukuntu iteje akaga kandi abantu batita ku byo ivuga".
Dukurikije uko Dr. Tom Frieden wahoze ari Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ikigo cyo muri Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara (CDC) yabivuze, icyo cyorezo cyari "ikintu kitari cyarateganyijwe".
Mu kiganiro cyatanzwe na CNN kuwa kabiri, yavuze ko "nta zindi virusi z'ubwandu zigeze zigaragara ku isi kuva aho zigeze".
Ghebreyesus yavuze ko "nta cyorezo cy'icyorezo cya coronavirus cyigeze kibaho ku isi".
Yongeyeho ati "kandi nta kibazo cy'isi yose twabonye".
Iki kibazo gishya cy'icyorezo cyibasiye isi cyaje nyuma y'uko mu kwezi kwa mbere OMS yafashe icyemezo cyo gutangaza ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo cyugarije isi yose.
Umuyobozi w'Ikigo cy'Igihugu cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Indwara Zandura n'Abaganga, Dr. Anthony Fauci, yavuze ko iki cyorezo "kigiye guhinduka, kandi ko nta kindi kizahinduka".
Ku wa kane, Associated Press yatangaje ko nibura ku isi hose hari abantu 126.000 banduye COVID-19, abagera ku 4.600 bakaba barapfuye.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-20 ni icyorezo gikomeje cy'indwara ya 2019 (COVID-19), iterwa na virusi itera indwara y'ubuhumekero yitwa severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Iki cyorezo cyamenyekanye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa mu Ukuboza 2019, cyatangazwa ko ari icyorezo cyugarije isi ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama 2020, cyemezwa ko ari icyorezo cyugarije isi ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 1.61 banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu 210 n'ahandi hantu, kandi abagera ku 97,000 bamaze gupfa.
Abantu bagera ku 364.000 barakize.
Imibare y'abapfuye mu Bushinwa igera kuri 4%, mu gihe mu Isi yose igera kuri 13.04% muri Alijeriya na .08% muri Nouvelle-Zélande.
Ibimenyetso bikunze kugaragara ni ibicurane, guhumeka no guhumeka umwuka.
Ibibazo by'iyi ndwara bishobora kuba birimo guhumeka cyane no guhumeka nabi.
Igihe cyo kwandura no kugaragaza ibimenyetso ni iminsi itanu ariko kuva ku minsi ibiri kugeza ku minsi cumi n'ine.
Nta muti w'iki cyorezo uzwi cyangwa umuti wo kurwanya iyi virusi.
Ubuvuzi bw'ibanze bugamije guhangana n'ibimenyetso by'uburwayi n'ubufasha buciriritse.Ibikorwa byo kwipimisha birimo, gukaraba intoki, gupfuka umunwa, kwigunga, kugenzura no kwitandukanya niba ukeka ko ufite uburwayi.
Abategetsi bo hirya no hino ku isi bitabiriye ibyo bitero bashyiraho amategeko yo kubuza abantu kujya mu mahanga, bashyiraho gahunda zo gushyira abantu mu kato, gukinga abantu, kwirinda mu kazi no gufunga ahantu hatandukanye.
Uyu muryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima n'ubukungu bw'abaturage ku isi hose, wahagaritse cyangwa wongera igihe cy'imikino, ibirori by'idini, ibya politiki n'umuco, ndetse no guteza ubukene bw'ibintu byatewe n'abantu bagura ibintu mu buryo buhenze.
Amashuri na za kaminuza byafunze ku rwego rw'igihugu cyangwa mu ntara mu bihugu 193, bigira ingaruka ku banyeshuri bagera kuri 99,4 ku ijana ku isi hose.
Amakuru atari yo ku byerekeye virusi y' corona yakwirakwiriye kuri interineti, kandi habayeho ibitero by'urwango n'ivangura ku Bashinwa, abandi baturage bo mu Burasirazuba no mu Majyepfo y'Uburasirazuba bwa Aziya cyangwa abantu b'amoko nk'ayo baturutse mu turere dufite icyorezo cy'iyi virusi.
Kubera ko ingendo n'inganda byafunzwe, umwuka n'umwuka wa karuboni byagabanutse.
Abashinzwe ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu Bushinwa (umurwa mukuru w'intara ya Hubei) batangaje ko hari abantu bake banduye icyorezo kitaramenyekana kuva ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, kandi ko iperereza ryatangiye mu ntangiriro za Mutarama 2020.
Abanduye bagaragaye ko batangiye kwandura mu isoko rya Huanan (isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja) bikekwa ko virusi yavuye mu nyamaswa igakwirakwira mu bantu.
Virusi yateye iyi ndwara yitwa SARS-CoV-2, ikaba ari virusi nshya ya SARS-CoV, ifite isano na virusi z'uruhu zitwa bat coronaviruses, pangolin coronaviruses na SARS-CoV. Umuntu wa mbere wanduye iyi ndwara yaje kugaragara nyuma yo kurwara ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019, kandi nta gihamya cy'uko uwo muntu yari afitanye isano n'ubucuruzi bw'ibikoresho by'ibanze.
Mu barwayi batangiye kugaragara mu kwezi k'Ukuboza 2019, bibiri bya gatatu by'abo barwayi bagaragaye ko bafitanye isano n'isoko.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, amakuru atazwi yaturutse mu kinyamakuru South China Morning Post yavuze ko umuntu wa mbere wafashwe ku ya 17 Ugushyingo 2019, ufite imyaka 55 wo mu ntara ya Hubei, ashobora kuba ari we wa mbere. Ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020, OMS yatangaje ko mu gihe abarwayi bashya bagabanutse mu Bushinwa ariko bakomeje kwiyongera mu Butaliyani, Irani na Koreya y'Epfo, umubare w'abarwayi bashya hanze y'Ubushinwa warenze uw'abarwayi bashya mu Bushinwa ku ncuro ya mbere.
Hari n'igihe abantu batavuga umubare nyawo w'abarwayi, cyane cyane abafite ibimenyetso byoroheje.
Ku ya 26 Gashyantare, umubare muto w'abanduye wavuzwe mu rubyiruko rw'imyaka 19 no munsi yayo, rugizwe na 2.4% by'abanduye ku isi. Umuyobozi w'ubujyanama mu bya siyansi mu Bwongereza, Patrick Vallance, yavuze ko 60% by'abaturage bo mu Bwongereza bashobora kwandura virusi mbere y'uko haboneka ubwoko bw'ubwandu bukomeye.
Abarwayi ni umubare w'abantu basuzumwe COVID-19, bagasuzumwa ko bafite virusi hakurikijwe imibare yemewe.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite abaturage barenga 3%, kandi ibihugu byinshi bifite gahunda yo kudakora ibizamini by'abatazifite ibimenyetso byoroheje, nka Ubutaliyani, Ubuholandi, Esipanye n'Ubuswise.
Ubushakashatsi bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe, bwagaragaje ko mu Bushinwa, kugeza ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, 86 ku ijana by'abanduye bari batarashyirirwaho urukingo, kandi ko 79 ku ijana by'abanduye bari batarashyirirwaho urukingo, bari baramaze kwandura.
Iperereza ku mibare ryashyizwe ahagaragara ku ya 30 Werurwe, ryagaragaje ko umubare w'abarwayi mu Butaliyani wari munini cyane kurusha uko byari byatangajwe.
Imibare y'ibanze y'ibanze (R0) ya COVID-19 yari 1.4 kugeza kuri 2.4.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'Ikigo cyo muri Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara no Kuzirinda, bwagaragaje ko icyo gitigiri gishobora kuba kigera kuri 5.7.
