Ku ya 22 Werurwe 2020, Ubudage bwahagaritse amateraniro y'abantu barenga babiri. Abantu bakuze n'abafite izindi ndwara zirimo diyabete, indwara z'umutima, indwara z'ubuhumekero, umuvuduko ukabije w'amaraso n'uburwayi bwo mu bwonko, bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, kandi CDC yasabye abantu kuguma mu rugo uko bishoboka kose cyane cyane mu turere dufite ubwandu. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, OMS n'izindi nzego z'ubuzima zatangiye gukoresha amagambo kwitarura abandi na kwishyiriraho intera mu gutangaza ko intego ari ukugabanya imikoranire ariko ko buri wese yagombye kwiherera ku wundi cyangwa ku wundi.
Gukoresha ijambo "kwitandukanya" byumvikanisha ko abantu bagomba kwitandukanya n'abandi, aho gushishikariza abantu gukomeza gushyikirana n'abandi mu bundi buryo.
Aka kazi ni ukubatera inkunga yo kugirana imibonano mpuzabitsina n'umuntu umwe gusa, utanduye cyangwa udafite ibimenyetso by'ubwandu.
Kwitarura abandi ni inama ku bantu basuzumwe ko banduye COVID-19 cyangwa abakekwaho kuba baranduye.
Inzego z'ubuzima zashyizeho amabwiriza yo kwitandukanya n'abandi. Leta nyinshi zisaba abantu cyangwa zikanasaba ko abantu bose baba mu turere twugarijwe n'icyorezo bajya mu kato.
Amabwiriza yo kwigunga cyane yatanzwe mu turere dufite ibyago byinshi.
Ababa baraganiriye n'umuntu ufite COVID-19 cyangwa abagiye mu bihugu cyangwa uturere dufite ubwandu bw'iyi ndwara basabwe kwiyicarira mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 uhereye igihe bashobora kuba baraganiriye n'umuntu ufite ubwandu.
Uburyo bwa mbere bwo kurwanya indwara z'ibicurane ni ukuzirwanya cyangwa kuzirwanya.
Gukumira bitangira mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo kandi bigamije gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abanduye no gushyiraho ingamba zo kurwanya no gukumira icyorezo mu rwego rwo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo mu baturage basigaye.
Iyo indwara idashobora gukwirakwira, imbaraga ziba zigarutse mu kurwanya indwara: hashyirwaho ingamba zo kugabanya ikwirakwira ryayo no gukumira ingaruka zayo ku buzima n'abaturage.
Uburyo bwo kwirinda no kurwana bishobora gukoreshwa icyarimwe.
Kugabanya ubwandu bisaba ko hafatwa ingamba zihamye kugira ngo haboneke ubwandu bushya mu gihe habayeho kugabanya ubwandu buri hasi ya 1. Uburyo bumwe bwo kurwanya ubwandu bw'indwara z'ibyorezo ni uguhagarika ubwandu bw'ubwandu bw'indwara z'ibyorezo mu kugerageza kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu bw'ubwandu bw'indwara z'ibyorezo mu buryo bworoshye, ibyo bikaba byitwa "flattening the curve".
Ibi bigabanya ibyago byo gukora cyane mu buvuzi kandi bigatuma haboneka igihe gihagije cyo gukora inkingo.
Ingamba z'ubuvuzi zidashingiye ku buvuzi zifasha kurwanya indwara z'ibyorezo zirimo, ingamba za bwite zo kwirinda indwara, nko gukaraba intoki, kwambara udupfukamunwa no kwitandukanya; ingamba za rubanda zo kwirinda abantu, nko gufunga amashuri no guhagarika amateraniro y'abantu benshi; gushishikariza abantu gukora imibonano mpuzabitsina; hamwe n'ingamba zo kwirinda ubwandu, nko gusukura ahantu no gukingira ibikoresho. Ingamba z'ubuvuzi zo kurwanya icyorezo zarakorewe mu Bushinwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo, nko gushyiraho gahunda yo gushyira abantu mu migi yose no gushyiraho amategeko yo kwirinda abantu.
Ibihugu byinshi byashyizeho andi mabwiriza agamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo.
Koreya y'Epfo yatangije gahunda yo gushyira abantu mu kato no kubacungira ubwabo, no kuburira abarwayi bari mu ngendo.
Singapore yafashije abamaze kwiyicarira mu gihe barwaye ibaha amafaranga, naho ababyanga ikabakira cyane.
Taiwan yongeye gukora udupfukamunwa no gukingira abantu bakoresha imiti. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'u Bwongereza na Amerika bugaragaza ko kwirinda (kugabanya indwara aho kuyihagarika) no kugabanya indwara (kugabanya indwara zitandura) ari imbogamizi zikomeye.
Uburyo bwo kurwanya indwara bushobora kugabanya umubare w'abantu bakenera ubuvuzi ku kigero cya 2/3 n'urupfu ku kigero cya 50%, ariko bigatuma abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi amagana bapfa, kandi indwara zikabura mu bitaro.
Kugabanya ubwandu bishobora kuba ingenzi cyane ariko bigomba gukorwa mu gihe virusi ikiri mu bantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzabonekera, niba ari rwo rwa mbere), ariko mu gihe indwara ishobora kugaruka mu gihe hakozwe ubushakashatsi.
Iyo hateganyijwe kurwanya indwara mu gihe kirekire, bigira ingaruka ku bantu kandi bigatuma batakaza amafaranga menshi.
Nta muti wa COVID-19 wemewe, ariko hari ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku miti irimo, harimo n'igerageza ry'imiti iriho ubu.
Kurya imiti ya grippe igurishwa mu maduka, kunywa ibinyobwa n'ikiruhuko bishobora kugabanya ibimenyetso byayo.
Bitewe n'akaga gashobora guteza, bishobora kuba ngombwa ko umuntu ahabwa umwuka, akanywa amazi, kandi agakoreshwa ibikoresho byo kumuhumeka.
Gukoresha imiti ya siporo bishobora gutuma ibintu birushaho kuzamba.
Imiti myinshi yari yarakoreshejwe mu kuvura izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi irimo gukorwaho ubushakashatsi ku mikoreshereze yayo mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS yavuze kandi ko "bimwe mu byiciro by'ubuvuzi gakondo bishobora kugabanya bimwe mu bimenyetso by'indwara ya SARS-CoV-19".
Kongera ubushobozi no guhindura uburyo bwo kuvura ku buryo buhuje n'ibikenewe ku barwayi ba COVID-19 nk'uko bisobanurwa na OMS ni intambwe ikomeye mu guhangana n'icyorezo.
ECDC n'ibiro by'umuryango w'abibumbye byita ku buzima (OMS) byashyizeho amabwiriza agenga ibitaro n'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze mu byiciro bitandukanye birimo gushyira imbaraga mu bikorwa by'igerageza mu gupima COVID-19, gukuraho ibikorwa bitari iby'ubutabazi igihe cyose bishoboka, gushyira mu kato no gushyira mu kato abarwayi ba COVID-19, no kongera ubuvuzi bwihariye binyuze mu guhugura abakozi no kongera umubare w'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'ibikoresho by'ibitaro.
Hari ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku byerekeye aho umurwayi wa mbere (witwa umurwayi wa zeru) yakomotse.
Umuntu wa mbere wanduye coronavirus itaramenyekana yageze ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi kumwe, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubei wariyongereye buhoro buhoro.
Ibi byari bifitanye isano n'isoko rya Huanan (Huanan Seafood Wholesale Market), ryagurishaga inyamaswa nzima, kandi hari igitekerezo cy'uko virusi yavuye muri imwe muri izi nyamaswa; cyangwa, mu yandi magambo, ko inkomoko yayo ari mu nyamaswa.
Ku ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan batangaje ko hari virusi ya "SARS coronavirus".
Abaganga umunani barimo Li Wenliang, bashinjwa na polisi ko bakwirakwizaga ibinyoma, naho undi witwa Ai Fen, ashinjwa n'abakoresha be ko yakubise abantu.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Ibitaro by'Umurenge wa Wuhan nyuma yaho yasohoye itangazo ku wa 31 Ukuboza, rivuga ko ryamenyesheje OMS.
Abategetsi b'i Wuhan bari bamaze kubimenyesha abarwayi benshi bafite ubwandu butaramenyekana, kugira ngo batangire gukora iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze mu bindi bice by'Ubushinwa, kubera ko umwaka mushya w'Ubushinwa ari wo wari utumye ikwirakwira ryayo rigabanuka cyane, kandi Wuhan ari umujyi w'imodoka nyinshi n'umuhanda wa gari ya moshi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwatangaje ko bwabonye abantu bashya 140 mu munsi umwe, barimo babiri i Beijing n'undi umwe i Shenzhen.
Nyuma y'aho, amakuru yemewe yagaragaje ko abantu 6,174 bari bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso by'iyo ndwara kugeza ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020. Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatsinze Ubushinwa mu mubare w'abanduye ku isi. Ku itariki ya 9 Mata 2020, abanduye barenga 1.61 bari bamaze kugaragara ku isi; abarenga 97,000 bari bamaze gupfa, naho 364,000 bari bamaze gukira.
Ibihugu bigera kuri 200 byamaze kwandura nibura umuntu umwe.
Kubera ko muri Afurika hari abantu benshi batagira aho baba, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byashyizeho amategeko agenga ingendo kandi byashyizeho n'imipaka.
Bimwe mu bihugu byashyizeho ingamba zo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo harimo guhagarika abantu (uzwi nka Guma mu Rugo, Guma mu Rugo cyangwa Guma mu Rugo) na Kafe.Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300, cyangwa hafi 90% by'abatuye Amerika bose bari bafite ubwandu bw'ubwoko bumwe, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 bari muri Filipine, miliyoni 59 muri Afurika y'Epfo, na miliyari 1.3 mu Buhinde.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi hose bari bafite ubumuga bwo kutabona, umubare ukaba wariyongereye cyane ugera kuri miliyari 2.6 nyuma y'iminsi ibiri, ni ukuvuga hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wa COVID-19 byitezwe ko yagaragaye ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan; amakuru y'ibanze agaragaza ko umuntu wa mbere wa mbere yabonetse ku ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Muganga Zhang Jixian yabonye itsinda ry'abarwayi bataramenyekana bamuherekeje ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, nyuma ibitaro byabimenyesheje abayobozi ba Wuhan Jianghan CDC ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ibipimo bya mbere by'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima byakozwe ku bantu banduye ku ya 27 Ukuboza 2019 byagaragaje ko banduye virusi ya SARS.
Itangazo ry'abaturage ryatanzwe n'ibitaro bya Wuhan Municipal Health Commission ku ya 31 Ukuboza.
OMS yamenyeshejwe kuri uwo munsi.
Nyuma y'uko ibyo bitangazwa, abapolisi baburiye abaganga bo muri Wuhan kubera ikwirakwizwa ry'inkuru y'uko hari icyorezo.
Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa yabanje kuvuga ko nta "amakuru y'ukuri" agaragaza ko abantu bashobora kwandura.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije gahunda ikomeye yiswe na Xi Jinping, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti mu Bushinwa, "intambara y'abaturage" yo kurwanya icyorezo.
Mu byiswe "guhagarika burundu" mu buzima bwa muntu, itegeko ryo gufunga ingendo ryatangajwe ku ya 23 Mutarama rihagarika ingendo zijya cyangwa ziva i Wuhan, rikongera gukwirakwizwa mu mijyi 15 yo mu ntara ya Hubei, rigira ingaruka ku bantu bagera kuri miliyoni 57.
Gukoresha imodoka bwite byari bibujijwe mu mujyi.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza Umwaka Mushya w'Abashinwa (itariki ya 25 Mutarama) byasubitswe mu duce twinshi.
Abayobozi batangaje kandi ko bagiye kubaka ibitaro by'agateganyo, Huoshenshan Hospital, byuzuye mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hubatswe ibitaro byitwaga Leishenshan, kugira ngo bivuriremo abarwayi benshi.
Uretse ibitaro bishya byubatswe, Ubushinwa bwahinduye n'ibindi bigo 14 i Wuhan, nk'aho abantu bakira inama, ibibuga by'umupira w'amaguru n'ibitaro by'igihe gito.Ku wa 26 Mutarama, leta yashyizeho andi mabwiriza yo kurwanya icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo no gutanga ibyangombwa by'abashoramari ku buzima bwabo no kongera iminsi mikuru y'ibiruhuko bya mbere by'umwaka.
Kaminuza n'amashuri hirya no hino mu gihugu na byo byafunzwe.
Hong Kong na Macau byashyizeho amategeko akomeye, cyane cyane ku mashuri n'amashuri makuru.
Mu bice byinshi by'Ubushinwa, hagiye hashyirwaho gahunda zo gukora akazi k'igihe gito.
Imihango yo gutembera yashyizweho mu gihugu no hanze ya Hubei.
Imihanda ya rusange yarahindutse, kandi ahantu ha kera ho gusura abantu hafunzwe mu gihe runaka.
Imihanda myinshi y'imijyi yashyizweho imipaka, kandi abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 760 (birenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abatuye isi) bashyizwe mu byiciro bitandukanye by'imipaka.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho iminsi 14 yo kwigunga ku banyamahanga bose binjira mu Bushinwa. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, mu Bushinwa hari umuntu umwe gusa wanduye mu minsi itanu ishize, kandi uyu yari umukozi wari uvuye i Istanbul agarutse i Guangzhou.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubushinwa Li Keqiang yatangaje ko icyorezo cya coronavirus mu Bushinwa cyafunzwe kandi ko icyorezo cy'iyi ndwara cyahagaritswe mu Bushinwa.
Kuri uwo munsi, ingamba zo guhagarika ingendo zongeye gushyirwa mu bikorwa muri Hubei, usibye Wuhan, nyuma y'amezi abiri hashyizweho gahunda yo gufunga. Minisiteri y'ububanyi n'amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020 ko viza zo kwinjira mu Bushinwa cyangwa impushya zo gukorerayo zizahagarikwa guhera ku ya 28 Werurwe, ariko ntibatangaza igihe izarangirira.
Abashaka kwinjira mu Bushinwa bazajya basaba viza ku biro by'u Bushinwa.
Guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yasabye abacuruzi n'abacuruzi gufungura ku itariki ya 30 Werurwe, ndetse no gushyiraho uburyo bwo guhumuriza ibigo by'ubucuruzi. Inama y'igihugu yatangiye gushyiraho umunsi wo gupfusha igihugu uhereye ku isaha ya 4 z'umugoroba tariki ya 4 Mata, mu gihe cyo kwizihiza umunsi mukuru wa Qingming, ariko leta y'igihangange yasabye imiryango gutanga ubutumwa bwo gupfusha ku rubuga rwa interineti mu rwego rwo kwirinda kongera gukwirakwiza COVID-19.
COVID-19 yemejwe ko yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020 avuye mu Bushinwa.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyavuze ko ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare, habaye ukwiyongera gukomeye kw'abarwayi, bivugwa ko byatewe n'inama yabereye i Daegu y'idini rishya ry'idini rya Shincheonji (Shincheonji Church of Jesus).
Abakurikiye Shincheonji bagiye i Daegu bavuye i Wuhan bakekwaho kuba ari bo batumye iki cyorezo cyandura.
Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bayoboke b'idini 9,336, 1,261 cyangwa 13% bavuze ko bafite ibimenyetso by'uburwayi. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko imibare y'ibanze y'uburwayi ari ku ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, muri Koreya hagezweho abantu barenga 2.000 banduye, ku itariki ya 29 Gashyantare habonekaga abantu 3.150.
Inzego zose za gisirikare muri Koreya y'Epfo zashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu basuzumwe bagaragaza ko banduye virusi.
Amabwiriza y'ingendo z'indege na yo yafashwe, bituma habaho impinduka. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho gahunda yafashwe nk'iyiganje kandi nziza ku isi yo kugenzura abantu banduye, gutandukanya abantu banduye, no gushyira mu kato abantu bose bahuye n'umuntu wafashwe na virusi.
Uburyo bwo gutoranya bwari bukubiyemo gutangaza ibimenyetso by'abimukira bakoresheje porogaramu za terefone, gutwara imodoka bajya mu kigo cyo gupima virusi bakibonera ibisubizo bukeye bwaho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima ku buryo hashobora gupimwa abantu 20.000 ku munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo yafashwe nk'igikorwa cy'iterambere mu kurwanya icyorezo nubwo atari imijyi yose yashyizwe mu kato.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko isaba Moon kuva ku butegetsi bavuga ko leta itita ku cyorezo mu gihe abandi bahakana ibyo yakoze.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Koreya y'Epfo ari yo yari ifite umubare muto w'abanduye mu byumweru bine.
Ku itariki ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku itariki ya 1 Mata, abagenzi bose baturutse mu bindi bihugu bazajya bashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku ya 1 Mata, ibigo by'itangazamakuru byatangaje ko Koreya y'Epfo yasabye inkunga y'ibikoresho byo gupima virusi mu bihugu 121.
Irani yatangaje ko ifite umurwayi wa mbere wa SARS-CoV-2 wabonetse ku ya 19 Gashyantare i Qom, kandi Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi bw'Ubuvuzi yatangaje ko abantu babiri bapfuye kuri uwo munsi.
Ingamba za mbere za leta zatangajwe harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibirori by'umuco, imikino, amasengesho yo ku wa gatanu, gufunga kaminuza, amashuri yisumbuye n'amashuri.
Irani yashyizeho miliyari eshanu z'amafaranga y'u Rwanda yo kurwanya virusi.
Ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020, Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato uturere twibasiwe n'iki cyorezo kandi ko abantu bagomba kujya mu kato.
Imyiteguro yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi itandukanye yatangajwe kuwa gatatu nubwo ingendo nyinshi z'ingenzi z'umwaka mushya w'Abaperesi (Persian New Year Nowruz) zakomeje.
Ibigo by'amasengesho bya Shiite i Qom byakomeje gufungurirwa abagenzi kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020.
Hagati y'ibyifuzo byo guhashya icyorezo cya Iran, ibihugu birenga icumi byari byatangaje abarwayi bari muri Irani ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, bigaragaza ko ubukana bw'iki cyorezo bwari hejuru y'abarwayi 388 leta ya Irani yari yavuze ko bari muri icyo gihugu ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yarahagaritswe, kuko abanyamuryango 23 kuri 290 bari barageragejwe ko banduye virusi ya Corona tariki ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku itariki ya 12 Gashyantare, umuryango uharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu Human Rights Watch wasabye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani kurekura abagizi ba nabi bose bazira uburenganzira bwa muntu nta nkomyi, no kurekura imfungwa zose zikwiye kurekurwa by'agateganyo.
Hari amakuru avuga ko hari ibyago byinshi byo kwandurira mu bigo by'abari mu ruhame, urugero nk'amabohero, aho usanga nta buvuzi buhagije buboneka.
Ku ya 15 Kanama, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye mu munsi umwe, ari na bwo bushya bukomeye bwabaye muri icyo gihugu kuva iki cyorezo cyatangira.
Ku itariki ya 17 y'ukwezi kwa gatatu, nibura abayobozi 12 ba mbere n'abari ku butegetsi muri Irani bari barapfuye bazize icyo cyorezo.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yari ifite abantu bashya 50 buri saha, kandi buri minota 10 hapfa umuntu umwe wanduye coronavirus.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'umukozi wa OMS, umubare w'abanduye muri Irani ushobora kuba wikubye inshuro eshanu.
Bivugwa kandi ko ibihano Amerika yafatiye Irani bishobora gutuma igihugu kidakomeza kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Komisiyo y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ishinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu yasabye ko inguzanyo z'amafaranga zatanzwe ku bihugu byibasiwe cyane na coronavirus, harimo na Irani, zakongera gushyirwa mu bikorwa.
