Ibipimo bya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) na SARS-CoV-2 birimo uburyo bwo kumenya virusi n'uburyo bwo kumenya udukoko tw'umubiri tw'umuntu wafashwe na virusi.
Uburyo bwo gupima virusi ni uburyo bwo gupima RT-PCR, ikora ubushakashatsi ku bwoko bwa RNA ya coronavirus.
Iki cyorezo cyatewe n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bwa RNA.
Ni ikimenyetso kigaragaza ko umuntu yaranduye cyangwa ko yaranduye.
Igikorwa cyo gupima udukoko tw'umubiri (serology) gishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima indwara cyangwa kumenya umubare w'abanduye.
Ibipimo by'abandura indwara bigaragaza umubare w'abanduye, harimo n'abatabyigaragazaga cyane ku buryo batagombaga kujya kwa muganga cyangwa abataragaragazaga ibimenyetso.
Umubare nyawo w'abantu bapfuye n'ubwandu bw'iyi ndwara bishobora kumenyekana hakoreshejwe ubu buryo.
Kubera gupima kutagira aho kugarukira, muri Werurwe 2020 nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru y'ukuri ku bijyanye n'ubwandu bwa virusi mu baturage bacyo.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyakoze ibizamini birenga 3% by'abaturage bacyo, kandi hari itandukaniro rinini mu mibare y'abamaze gukorerwa ibizamini hirya no hino ku isi.
Ibyo bishobora gutuma umubare w'abapfa urushaho kwiyongera, bikaba bishobora gutuma umubare w'abapfa wiyongera mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo kuvura polymérase mu gihe nyacyo (rRT-PCR), ibipimo bishobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'amaraso bivuye mu buryo butandukanye, harimo guterwa mu mazuru no mu mazuru cyangwa mu bipimo by'ibinure.
Ingaruka zikunze kuboneka mu masaha make cyangwa mu minsi ibiri.
Iperereza rya RT-PCR hamwe n'ubushakashatsi bw'ibinyabiziga by'ubwonko bw'umuntu, byemewe gukorwa mu cyumweru cya mbere gusa cy'uburwayi.
Nyuma y'aho, iyo mikorobe ishobora gutakara mu muhogo, mu gihe ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha.
Ku barwayi basuzumwe mu cyumweru cya kabiri, ibipimo bishobora gukurwa mu mitsi binyuze mu gukoresha catétere cyangwa se se se ku buryo bw'ibanze.
Imwe mu miti ya mbere ya PCR yatangijwe muri Charité i Berlin muri Gashyantare 2020 ikoresheje uburyo bwo kwinjiza polymerase mu gihe nyacyo (rRT-PCR), ituma haboneka ibikoresho 250,000 by'imiti byatanzwe n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS).
Ubwongereza na bwo bwari bwaratangije uburyo bwo gupima ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020. Ikigo cyo muri Koreya y'Epfo cya Kogenebiotech cyatangije uburyo bwo gupima SARS-CoV-2 bushingiye kuri PCR (PowerChek Coronavirus) ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020.
