Ibipimo by'uburyo bubiri ntibyari byemewe kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020, kandi kugeza icyo gihe, ibipimo bya leta n'ibya leta ntibyari byemewe gutangira gupima.
Ibipimo byemejwe n'ikigo gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti (Food and Drug Administration) mu rwego rw'ubuziranenge (Emergency Use Authorization).
