Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi.
Nyuma yo guhindura impamba cyangwa gukaraba umwana, mva mu bwiherero.
Nyuma yo gukata, gukata cyangwa gukata.
Nyuma yo gukora ku matungo, ku biribwa by'amatungo cyangwa ku birungo by'amatungo.
Isuku y'amaboko mu buvuzi ni ukwirinda kwanduza intoki mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gutanga imiti cyangwa kuvurwa bishobora kugabanya ubwandu.
Intego y'ibanze yo gukaraba intoki ni ukwica mikorobe (bakteriya, virusi cyangwa izindi mikorobe zishobora gutera indwara) no kuvanaho imiti ishobora guteza indwara cyangwa uburwayi.
Ibi ni ingenzi cyane ku bantu bakora mu bijyanye n'ibiribwa cyangwa mu by'ubuzima, ariko ni byiza ku bantu bose.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kanini, harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ibicurane, coronavirus, n'izindi ndwara zandurira mu bandi; kwirinda ibintu byangiza; kugabanya indwara zandura;
no kugabanya umubare w'abana bapfa mu gihe cyo kubyarira mu rugo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2013 bwagaragaje ko kongera imyitwarire yo gukaraba intoki bishobora gutuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu batera imbere.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, umubare w'abana bapfa bazize indwara z'ibicurane n'isukari ushobora kugabanuka binyuze mu guhindura imyitwarire, urugero nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Icyo gikorwa cyoroshye gishobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa bazize iyi ndwara ku kigero cya 50%.
Guteza imbere isuku y'amaboko bishobora kugabanya umwanda ku kigero cya kimwe cya gatatu, bikaba ari kimwe na gahunda yo gutanga amazi meza mu baturage bafite amikoro make.
Kugabanya ubukana bw'ubwandu ku kigero cya 48% bishobora guterwa no gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni bwo buryo bwiza kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda ubwandu bw'ubwandu, nk'uko bikorwa mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu baturage hirya no hino ku isi.
Indwara y'igituntu, ari na yo ndwara yica kurusha izindi, ni yo ihitana abana benshi bari munsi y'imyaka itanu, ihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 1.8 buri mwaka.
Indwara y'igituntu n'iy'igituntu byombi bihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 3,5 buri mwaka.
Nk'uko UNICEF ibivuga, gukaraba intoki n'isabune mbere yo kurya na nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero ni umuco w'abantu ushobora kurokora ubuzima bw'abantu benshi kurusha inkingo cyangwa imiti, bigatuma umubare w'abapfa bazize indwara z'ibicurane ugabanukaho kimwe cya kane.
Gukaraba intoki akenshi bijyana n'indi myitozo y'isuku nk'imwe mu mishinga y'amazi, isuku n'isuku (WASH).
Gukaraba intoki kandi bifasha kwirinda indwara z'uruhu zitwa diarrhoea, zikwirakwira iyo umuntu afashe undi.
Akaga gato ko gukaraba intoki buri gihe ni ugukora ku ruhu rw'umubiri cyangwa kuruma.
Ubushakashatsi bwakorewe muri Danimarike mu mwaka wa 2012, bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutuma umuntu agira ikibazo cy'uruhu rw'intoki, cyitwa eczema cyangwa dermatite y'intoki, kandi akenshi usanga abaganga bakunze kuvuga ko ari indwara y'uruhu rw'intoki.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi na byo bifatwa nk'ikimenyetso cy'indwara yo guhora utekereza cyane (obsession compulsive disorder, OCD).
Hari ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi mu gihe cy'amanywa aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ngombwa kugira ngo umuntu atagerwaho n'indwara z'amaraso: nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero (kubyutsa, kwisiga), nyuma yo gukaraba umwana (kuhindura impapuro), mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya na nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gukora ku nyama cyangwa amafi mabi.
Indi mimerere yo gukaraba intoki neza kugirango wirinde gukwirakwiza indwara ni mbere cyangwa nyuma yo gukora ku byondo cyangwa imbwa; nyuma yo gukorora, gukorora, cyangwa gukorora; nyuma yo gukora ku byondo by'inyamaswa cyangwa ku nyamaswa; na nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, abantu ntibakunda gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Ubushakashatsi ku gukaraba intoki mu bihugu 54 mu 2015 bwerekanye ko ku kigereranyo, 38.7% by'ingo zakoreshaga isabune mu gukaraba intoki. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2014 bwagaragaje ko Arabiya Sawudite ari yo yakoreshaga isabune mu gukaraba intoki ku kigero cya 97%; Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zari hagati na 77%, naho Ubushinwa bwari hasi na 23%. Muri iki gihe hari uburyo bwinshi bwo guhindura imyitwarire y'abantu kugira ngo bongere umuco wo gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu gihe cy'ibihe bigoye. Gukaraba intoki mu matsinda mu gihe cy'amasomo ku munsi ni kimwe mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere yo kwinjiza imikorere y'abana mu bwonko.
