Mu kwirinda indwara z'ubwandu bw'ubumara bwa staphylococcal mu bitaro, byabonetse ko inyungu nyinshi zo gukaraba intoki zaturutse ku bice 20% by'ibanze by'aho umuntu yakarabye, naho izindi nyungu nke cyane zaturutse ku kwiyuhagira intoki byongereyeho 35%.
Gukaraba n'isabune gusa byongera inshuro zirenga eshatu ubwandu bw'ibinyabutabire mu byokurya ugereranyije no gukaraba n'isabune irimo umuti wica mikorobe. Kugereranya gukaraba intoki n'isuku irimo umuti wica mikorobe mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30 byerekanye ko gukaraba intoki n'isuku irimo umuti wica mikorobe mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30 byerekana ko gukaraba intoki n'isuku irimo umuti wica mikorobe mu gihe cy'amasegonda 26 byagabanyije mikorobe mu gihe cy'amasegonda arenga abiri ugereranyije no gukaraba n'isuku irimo umuti wica mikorobe.
Ahubwo, isabune n'amazi ni byo bifasha cyane kurusha imiti yo guhanagura imyanda irimo inzoga mu kugabanya virusi ya H1N1 influenza A na Clostridium difficile spores mu ntoki. Ingamba zo guteza imbere isuku y'intoki mu bitaro zishobora kuba zikubiyemo kwigisha abakozi gukaraba intoki, kongeramo imiti yo guhanagura imyanda irimo inzoga, no kwibutsa abakozi mu nyandiko cyangwa mu magambo.
Hakenewe ubushakashatsi bwimbitse ku buryo bwo kuvura indwara zitandukanye.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, gukaraba intoki n'isabune bifatwa nk'uburyo bwo kugabanya amafaranga, kugira ubuzima bwiza, no kugira ibyokurya byiza.
Nyamara, kubura amazi, isabune cyangwa ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu ngo, ku mashuri no ku kazi, bituma bidashoboka gukwirakwiza no kumenyekanisha umuco wo gukaraba intoki.
Urugero, mu bice byinshi by'Afurika byo mu cyaro, ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki hafi y'ubwiherero bwa bwite cyangwa bwa rusange birahari, nubwo hari uburyo buhendutse bwo kubaka aho gukaraba intoki.
Ahubwo, gukaraba intoki mu rugero ruto bishobora kuba ari umuco umuntu yashinze kera, aho kuba ari ikibazo cy'amazi n'isabune.
Gutangaza no gukangurira abantu gukaraba intoki n'isabune bishobora guhindura imyanzuro y'igihugu, kwigisha abantu akamaro ko gukaraba intoki no guhindura imyitwarire y'abantu mu gihe cy'ubuzima bwabo bwose.
Ariko kugira ngo ibyo bigerweho neza, ni ngombwa kugenzura no kugenzura ibyo abantu bakora.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku nshuro 70 bwagaragaje ko gahunda z'imibereho y'abaturage mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere (LMICs) zigira ingaruka nziza mu gushishikariza abantu gukaraba intoki; mu by'ukuri, ni gahunda yo gukaraba intoki mu gihe nta cyo ikora. Urugero ni "Inzira y'Inyenyeri eshatu" ya UNICEF; iyi gahunda ikubiyemo gushishikariza amashuri gukoresha uburyo bworoshye kandi buhendutse mu gushishikariza abanyeshuri gukaraba intoki n'isabune, nk'imwe mu nshingano z'isuku.
Iyo amanota y'ibanze agezweho, amashuri ashobora kuva ku inyenyeri imwe akagera ku eshatu.
Gushyiraho ahantu hakwiye ho gukaraba intoki bishobora kuba kimwe mu bintu by'ingenzi mu rwego rwo kugabanya indwara n'urupfu rw'abana.
Umunsi mpuzamahanga wo gukaraba intoki ni urugero rwiza rwo gushishikariza abantu guhindura imyitwarire. Kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-2020, UNICEF yashyizeho urubuga rwo gushishikariza abantu gukaraba intoki.
Hari ubushakashatsi buke cyane bwagaragaje ubushobozi bw'amafaranga y'abaturage mu gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere ugereranyije n'ibipimo bya DALY byirindwa.
Nyamara, ubushakashatsi bumwe bugaragaza ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari byo by'ingenzi kurusha ibindi bikorwa byose by'isuku n'amazi.
