Ibibazo by'akazi biterwa na COVID-19
Ingamba zo kwirinda ibibazo by'akazi biterwa na COVID-19 ni ugushyiraho ingamba zo kwirinda impanuka n'uburyo bwo kwirinda kwandura icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Uburyo bwiza bwo kwirinda impanuka zo mu kazi bushingiye ku hantu umuntu akorera akazi, kandi ibibazo by'ingorabahizi biterwa no kumenya aho impanuka zaturuka, urugero rw'icyorezo mu karere, n'ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19.
Dukurikije Itegeko ry'Umutekano n'Ubuzima mu Mirimo rya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika (OSHA), akazi gafite ibyago bike gafite aho gahuriye n'abantu n'abandi bakozi, kandi ibyo bishobora kugabanyirizwa n'ubuvuzi bworoheje, gukangurira abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, guhumeka neza, no gukora isuku buri gihe n'isukura ry'ibinyabuzima.
Ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi bifite ibyago bike harimo n'ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi bigizwe n'abantu bahuye n'abantu bataramenyekana cyangwa bakekwaho kuba barwaye COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura bitewe n'uko bakwirakwije indwara mu karere cyangwa mu bihugu by'amahanga.
Muri ibyo hakubiyemo n'abakozi bakorana n'abandi, urugero nk'amashuri, aho bakorera n'amaduka.
Gukumira ubwandu muri rusange harimo ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda indwara, harimo gukoresha ibikoresho by'isuku, no kwambara imyenda yo kwikingira mu gihe hari umurwayi wa COVID-19 uri hafi.
Itegeko rya OSHA rivuga ko abaganga/abaforomo bakora mu bigo by'abashidikanya kuri COVID-19 bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, kandi ko iyo ibyago biba byinshi iyo abo bakozi bafashe ibipimo by'umubiri w'umuntu wapfuye cyangwa ukekwaho COVID-19.
Mu byo abakozi bakora harimo kwirinda akaga, harimo uburyo bwo kubaka, nko kwirinda ko umwuka uva mu cyumba ujya mu kindi, no kwirinda ko umuntu yakora akazi runaka.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kubura akazi kubera uburwayi, kubera ko baba bakeneye kwita ku bandi, cyangwa se kubera gutinya ko bashobora kurwara.
Ubucuruzi bushobora guhinduka, haba ku byo abantu bifuza ndetse n'uburyo bwo kugura (urugero: kugura mu gihe cy'ibihe by'ibiciro by'ibicuruzwa cyangwa gushaka kugura ibintu bakeneye cyangwa kudasohoka mu modoka iyo bageze aho ibicuruzwa biri).
Icya nyuma, gutwara ibicuruzwa biturutse mu turere twugarijwe na COVID-19 bishobora guhungabana. Kwitegura no kwirinda icyorezo ni ngombwa kugira ngo dufashe kuyobora ibikorwa byo kucyirinda.
Iyo gahunda igenzura ibipimo by'ibyago byugarije ahantu h'akazi hamwe n'akazi ubwako, harimo ingaruka zo gukingirwa, ibyago bituruka mu rugo no mu baturage, n'izindi ngaruka ziterwa n'imyaka cyangwa indwara zidakira.
