Kwitegura indwara zandura bishobora guterwa n'amafaranga igihugu cyose cyangwa akarere kose gasaba.
Intego zo kurwanya indwara z'ibyorezo harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byo kwandura indwara z'ibyorezo, gukomeza ibikorwa, no kugabanya ingaruka ku bantu bafatanyabikorwa mu bikorwa byabo.
Indwara y'icyorezo mu karere k'ubucuruzi irarambiwe cyane.
Guteganya ibibazo ni uburyo bukoreshwa cyane ku isi mu gutunganya ibibazo mu kazi no mu buzima, mu gushyira mu byiciro uburyo bukoreshwa hakurikijwe ibyiza bwabwo.
