Ingirabuzimafatizo ihindura angiotensin 2 (ACE2) ni ingirabuzimafatizo ifata ku gice cy'umubiri (ku ruhu rw'umubiri) ku mubiri w'umuntu mu maraso, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu maraso.
ACE2 irwanya ingirabuzimafatizo ihindura angiotensin (ACE) igabanya ingano ya angiotensin-II ikura Ang ((1-7)), bigatuma iba umuti ushobora gukoreshwa mu kurwanya indwara z'umutima. ACE2 kandi ikora nk'intangiriro yo kwinjira mu mubiri mu mikorobe zimwe na zimwe.
Mu bantu, iyi poroteyine yitwa hACE2.
Ingirabuzimafatizo ya angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 ni ingirabuzimafatizo irimo zinc iboneka ku maso y'ingirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso n'izindi.
Poroteyine ya ACE2 ni N-terminal peptidase M2 domain na C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 isohora rimwe mu mubiri, ibice byayo by'ingenzi bigaragarira ku maso y'ibinyugunyugu n'izindi nsina.
Urusobe rw'umushongi wa ACE2 ruterwa ku ruhu n'ikinyabutabire cyitwa sheddase, maze amazi yavuye muri iyo poroteyine akajya mu maraso, nyuma yaho akaza guhinduka umusemburo.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifata ku ruhu rw'ingirabuzimafatizo cyane cyane mu bice by'uruhu by'uruhu rwa kabiri, mu bice by'uruhu ruto, mu mitsi no mu maraso, no mu bice by'amaraso.
ACE2 mRNA iboneka kandi mu bice by'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ibumoso, mu gice cy'inyuma cy'ubwonko, no mu gice cy'ibumoso.
