Nk'imikorere ya poroteyine itwara umubiri, ACE2 ikora nk'inzira y'ingenzi yo kwinjira mu bwisanzure bw'ubwandu bwa virusi zimwe na zimwe za corona, harimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi itera SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi itera COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, kwihuza kwa poroteyine ya S1 ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 ku gice cy'ingenzi cya ACE2 ku gice cy'umubiri bituma virusi n'ibindi bice by'umubiri bikurwa aho byari byarahoze bikagaruka mu bice by'umubiri.
Ubu buryo bwo kwinjira kandi bukeneye kuvugurura poroteyine ya S na serine protease TMPRSS2, ubu buryo bwo kuvugurura bukaba bukomeje gusuzumwa kugira ngo harebwe niba bushobora gukoreshwa mu buvuzi. Ibi byatumye bamwe bavuga ko kugabanya umubare wa ACE2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo, bishobora gufasha kurwanya indwara.
