Ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ko bigiye gufatanya mu gushyigikira porogaramu ya Bluetooth kuri Android na iOS mu buryo butaziguye mu bikoresho byabo bya elegitoroniki.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa, ifatanyije na Alipau, yatangije porogaramu ituma abaturage bayo bashobora kureba niba hari abantu bahuye na COVID-19.
Iyo porogaramu ikoreshwa mu migi isaga 200 yo mu Bushinwa.
Porogaramu yakozwe n'abakozi ba IT bo muri ako gace, yashyizwe ahagaragara kandi igomba gukoreshwa na buri wese kandi izahabwa leta. Macedonia y'Amajyaruguru yatangije porogaramu ya "StopKorona!", porogaramu ya Bluetooth yo gukurikirana abanduye n'abashobora kuba barwaye no kohereza amakuru yihuse ku buvuzi n'ubuyobozi.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe n'ubushikiranganji bw'itumanaho n'ikoranabuhanga hamwe n'ubushikiranganji bw'ubuzima.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 14 Mata 2020, iyi porogaramu itegerejwe kwemezwa na Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, leta yatangaje ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abarwayi yari mu cyiciro cya nyuma cy'iterambere, kandi ko izaba imaze ibyumweru bike itangiye gukoreshwa. Porogaramu ikurikirana iri gukorwa muri Irlande, mu Bufaransa ("StopCovid").
Australia na Nouvelle Zélande zirimo gusuzuma porogaramu za TraceTogether za Singapore na BlueTrace protocol.Uburusiya burateganya gutangiza porogaramu ya geofencing ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bahuye na virusi i Moscou, igamije kubarinda kuva mu rugo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu muri kaminuza ya Cambridge wigisha iby'umutekano, yavuze ko hari ibibazo by'imikoreshereze y' porogaramu, harimo no kumva ko ikora neza cyangwa se ko idakora neza iyo porogaramu ikoreshwa n'abantu benshi.
Mu rwego rwo gukemura ikibazo cya porogaramu za coronavirus z'ibinyoma cyangwa zangiza, Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku byiciro by'ibigo bishobora gushyira porogaramu zijyanye na coronavirus kuri App Store, byemerera gusa ibigo byemewe cyangwa ibigo byemewe.
