Iyi gahunda yageragejwe kuri SARS ariko ibisubizo byayo ntibyari birangiye.
Kugabanya ubukana bw'agakoko gatera SARS-CoV-2 ni uburyo bwo kuvura hakoreshejwe agakoko gatera SARS-CoV-2.
Hari ubundi buryo bushoboka, urugero nk'imiti yica udukoko twitwa antibody-dependent cellular cytotoxicity na/cyangwa phagocytosis.
Hari ubundi buryo bwo kuvura abarwayi butandukanye, urugero nko gukoresha abarwayi batandukanye bitwa monoclonal, burimo gukorwa.
Igikoresho cyo kuvura amaraso, gikubiyemo amaraso y'abarwayi bakize kandi kigakoreshwa mu kurwanya virusi, gishobora kongerwaho kugira ngo hakorwe indi miti.
Indwara ya Coronavirus, itsinda ry'ibimenyetso
Li Wenliang, umuganga mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan, yaje kwandura COVID-19 nyuma y'igihe gito apfuye nyuma yo gutangaza ko yanduye.
